
WEBVTT

01:12.790 --> 01:23.010
教父

01:17.010 --> 01:23.010
第2部

01:49.330 --> 01:51.920
(教父的原名是 维多安东里尼)</br>

01:51.930 --> 01:54.480
(诞生在西西里岛 的柯里昂村)</br>

01:54.490 --> 01:57.080
(1901年时  他的父亲)</br>

01:57.090 --> 01:59.610
(因侮辱当地的 黑手党老大被谋杀)</br>

01:59.620 --> 02:02.220
(他的兄长保罗发誓要复仇)</br>

02:02.230 --> 02:04.780
(却在山区里失去踪影)</br>

02:04.790 --> 02:07.590
(留下了维多在那儿)</br>

02:07.600 --> 02:09.780
(成为唯一男性)</br>

02:09.790 --> 02:12.390
(在葬礼中陪伴他的母亲)</br>

02:12.400 --> 02:14.680
(他当时才九岁)</br>

02:58.830 --> 03:03.490
他们杀了那个孩子</br>
They've killed the boy!

03:03.500 --> 03:07.720
他们杀了年轻的保罗</br>
They've killed young Paolo!

03:07.730 --> 03:10.420
他们杀了你的儿子保罗</br>
They've killed your son Paolo!

03:10.430 --> 03:15.500
凶手!…</br>
Murderers! Murderers!

03:27.700 --> 03:33.500
我的儿子!</br>
My son...

03:40.440 --> 03:43.900
我的儿子!</br>
My son...

04:09.750 --> 04:12.070
我尊敬的西西欧阁下</br>
All my respect, Don Ciccio.

04:14.510 --> 04:16.200
西西欧阁下…</br>
Don Ciccio...

04:16.210 --> 04:20.840
你因我丈夫不肯 向你屈服而杀他</br>
You killed my husband because he wouldn't give in to you.

04:20.850 --> 04:23.910
以及他的长子保罗</br>
And his oldest son Paolo...

04:23.920 --> 04:26.780
因为他誓言要复仇</br>
because he swore revenge.

04:26.790 --> 04:32.140
但维多是我仅有的 而且笨手笨脚</br>
But Vito is only nine.And dumb-witted.

04:32.150 --> 04:33.810
他从来不说话</br>
He never speaks.

04:33.820 --> 04:36.750
我怕的不是他的话</br>
It's not his words I'm afraid of.

04:37.690 --> 04:42.880
他很弱  不可能伤害任何人</br>
He's weak. He couldn't hurt anyone.

04:42.890 --> 04:45.620
但他长大后会变得很强</br>
But when he grows, he'll grow strong.

04:45.630 --> 04:49.990
别担心 这小孩不会对你怎么样</br>
Don't worry. This little boy can't do a thing to you.

04:56.730 --> 05:01.370
当他长大以后会回来报仇的</br>
When he's a man, he'll come for revenge.

05:01.930 --> 05:04.260
我求你  西西欧阁下</br>
I beg you, Don Ciccio,spare my only son.

05:04.270 --> 05:06.870
放了我唯一的孩子</br>
He's all I have left.

05:06.900 --> 05:09.230
他是我仅有的了</br>
He's all I have left.

05:09.270 --> 05:13.060
我对天发誓 他永远不会伤害你</br>
I swear to God he'll never do you any harm.

05:13.070 --> 05:15.440
放了他吧!</br>
Spare him!

05:20.050 --> 05:21.820
不行</br>
No.

05:23.580 --> 05:25.470
快逃  维多</br>
Run, Vito!

05:25.480 --> 05:27.540
别动否则我杀了你!</br>
Move and I'll kill him!

05:27.550 --> 05:31.540
快逃!维多</br>
Run, Vito!

05:33.050 --> 05:39.820
杀了他!…</br>
Kill him...

05:42.560 --> 05:51.120
任何家庭收容了维多安东里尼 都会后悔的</br>
Any family who hides the boy Vito Andolini will regret it!

05:52.260 --> 05:55.290
你们明白吗?</br>
You understand?

05:58.460 --> 06:05.230
任何收容维多安东里尼的 都会有麻烦</br>
Anybody who hides the boy

06:05.240 --> 06:11.940
任何人收容了维多安东里尼…</br>
If anyone is hiding the boy Vito Andolini...

06:13.580 --> 06:18.270
把他交给我们</br>
...turn him over to us.

06:18.280 --> 06:22.200
西西欧阁下会谢谢你的 那对你及那孩子都好</br>
Don Ciccio will thank you for it!

06:29.910 --> 06:33.940
任何人收容了维多安东里尼…</br>
Any family who hides the boy Vito Andolini...

06:33.950 --> 06:37.580
维多  我们会为你祈祷的</br>
Vito, we're praying for you!

06:39.380 --> 06:46.180
任何收容维多安东里尼的 都会有麻烦</br>
Anybody who hides the boy Vito Andolini is in for trouble!

06:46.190 --> 06:48.810
把他交给我们</br>
Turn him over to us.

06:48.820 --> 06:53.210
西西欧阁下会谢谢你的</br>
Don Ciccio will thank you for it!

06:53.220 --> 07:01.390
那对你及那孩子都好</br>
It'll be better for the boy,and better for you!

07:08.100 --> 07:15.930
任何人收容了维多安东里尼…</br>
Any family who hides the boy Vito Andolini...

08:46.180 --> 08:47.740
去找护士</br>
Nurse.

09:17.030 --> 09:18.350
翻译员</br>
Interpreter!

09:25.130 --> 09:26.920
你从哪里来?</br>
Where are you from?

09:27.900 --> 09:29.760
你叫什么名字?</br>
What is your name?

09:34.270 --> 09:38.100
说吧!孩子  你叫什么名字?</br>
Come on, son. What is your name?

09:38.110 --> 09:40.610
你叫什么名字</br>
What is your name?

09:44.140 --> 09:47.410
由柯里昂村来的维多安东里尼</br>
Vito Andolini from Corleone.

09:47.840 --> 09:51.070
柯里昂  维多柯里昂</br>
Corleone. Vito Corleone.

09:51.080 --> 09:54.640
好了  到那边去</br>
Okay, over there.

09:54.650 --> 09:56.470
下一位</br>
Next.

09:57.050 --> 09:58.620
叫什么名字</br>
Your name?

10:05.150 --> 10:09.180
告诉他他有天花 要隔离三个月</br>
Tell him he has smallpox. Quarantine three months.

10:18.690 --> 10:24.330
维多柯里昂?…</br>
Vito Corleone!Vito Corleone!

10:25.530 --> 10:28.160
在这!他就是</br>
Here he is. This is him.

11:02.550 --> 11:09.250
(1901年  爱丽丝岛 维多柯里昂)</br>

11:20.390 --> 11:23.280
(他的孙子 安东尼维多柯里昂)</br>

11:23.290 --> 11:28.790
(1958年  大浩湖 内华达州)</br>

12:14.760 --> 12:17.210
泰德!把车钥匙拿来</br>
Did you bring the car keys?

12:19.380 --> 12:22.350
洛莉!…</br>
Laurie! Laurie!

12:41.970 --> 12:43.460
妈妈!</br>
Mama!

12:45.230 --> 12:46.730
妈妈!</br>
Mama!

12:49.070 --> 12:50.360
看看是谁在这</br>
Look,who's here?

12:50.370 --> 12:51.950
-柯梅诺神父! -康妮  你好</br>
- Father Carmelo.-

12:51.960 --> 12:54.060
-这位是柯梅诺神父 -我是梅尔强森</br>
- This is Father Carmelo. - I'm Merle Johnson.

12:54.070 --> 12:55.660
是这教区的神父</br>
family parish.

12:56.970 --> 13:00.630
妈妈!我回来了</br>
Mama!Here I am.

13:00.640 --> 13:02.500
我真搞不懂</br>
Constanzia,

13:02.510 --> 13:03.900
你来迟了一个星期?</br>
after one week?

13:03.910 --> 13:07.870
我上星期派车去机场接你</br>
I sent the car to the airport last week to pick you up.

13:08.020 --> 13:09.170
那是场大灾难</br>
It was chaos.

13:09.180 --> 13:11.540
反正我回来了 只是迟了一星期罢了</br>
Anyway, here I am, just one week late.

13:11.550 --> 13:14.370
这个是送给妈妈的</br>
This is for my mama!

13:14.380 --> 13:16.410
-这是什么? -你还记得梅尔吧?</br>
- What is this? - You remember Merle?

13:16.420 --> 13:17.570
你好  妈妈</br>
Hello,mama.

13:17.580 --> 13:20.010
你好吗?谢谢你</br>
Hello. How are you? Thank you.

13:20.150 --> 13:22.170
麦克在哪?我得和他谈谈</br>
Where's Michael? I gotta to talk to him,

13:22.180 --> 13:23.380
把几件事弄清楚</br>
and um, get a few things straight,

13:23.390 --> 13:25.180
我不能排队见他</br>
and I can't wait on line.

13:25.790 --> 13:28.340
你先去看你的孩子</br>
You go see your children first.

13:28.350 --> 13:34.250
然后再操心见你弟弟的事 你得和别人一样排队</br>
Then you worry about waiting on line to see your brother. Like everybody else.

13:38.790 --> 13:40.690
各位先生女士</br>
Ladies and gentlemen...

13:42.100 --> 13:45.520
我们最尊贵的来宾 想要说几句话</br>
A most distinguished guest would like to say a few words.

13:45.530 --> 13:48.090
请欢迎内华达州的参议员</br>
Please welcome Senator Pat Geary

13:48.100 --> 13:49.800
派特葛瑞</br>
of the State of Nevada.

13:49.860 --> 13:52.290
还有葛瑞太太</br>
And there is Mrs. Geary.

14:03.200 --> 14:05.300
非常谢谢各位先生女士</br>
Thank you very much, Ladies and Gentlemen

14:05.310 --> 14:12.370
对于我及内人而言 今天是个非常快乐的日子</br>
This is a very, very happy day for me and my wife Mrs. Geary.

14:12.510 --> 14:15.900
我们极少回来内华达州</br>
We see Nevada far too seldom.

14:15.910 --> 14:19.730
我们今天回来特别高兴 一来和老朋友相聚</br>
But today we can join with old friends,

14:19.740 --> 14:20.970
二来我们能交到新的朋友</br>
we can make new friends,

14:20.980 --> 14:25.400
三则是共同庆祝一个年轻人 首度领圣餐礼</br>
and we help celebrate a young man's first Communion.

14:25.410 --> 14:32.540
而且也要谢谢那孩子的家庭 对于本州慷慨的捐献</br>
And also to thank that boy's family for a magnificent contribution to the State.

14:32.550 --> 14:35.480
我手上有张支票</br>
I have here in my hand a cheque

14:35.860 --> 14:38.320
受款人是州立大学</br>
made out to the university,

14:38.330 --> 14:41.150
而且金额惊人</br>
and it is a magnificent endowment

14:41.160 --> 14:48.190
是以安东尼维多柯里昂的 名义捐赠的</br>
in the name of Anthony Vito Corleone.

14:48.460 --> 14:53.100
钱是安东尼父母捐出来我们有</br>
The cheque is signed by that young man's parents,

14:53.100 --> 14:57.720
请这对善长站起来和大家见面</br>
whom I think we should recognise.

14:57.870 --> 14:59.150
请站起来 让大伙们能看到你们</br>
Mike, Pat, Kay. stand up, please. Let the folks see you!

14:59.160 --> 15:01.360
各位  希望大家和我一起</br>
Folks, I want you to join me

15:01.370 --> 15:07.660
向麦克柯里昂先生夫人致谢</br>
in giving a real Nevada thank you to Mr. and Mrs. Michael Corleone!

15:12.970 --> 15:16.260
我们同时有一个 特别安排的节目</br>
We also have, as a special added attraction,

15:16.270 --> 15:18.330
西耶华儿童合唱团</br>
the Sierra Boys Choir,

15:18.340 --> 15:23.300
他们特别挑选了一些歌曲</br>
who have chosen a certain special song

15:23.310 --> 15:26.370
为这里的主人麦克柯里昂</br>
and a special arrangement to

15:26.380 --> 15:28.640
所特别安排的</br>
honour their host, Mr. Michael Corleone.

15:28.810 --> 15:30.420
孩子们!</br>
Boys.

15:47.130 --> 15:48.610
匾额</br>
The plaque.

15:49.160 --> 15:51.480
对了</br>
Relax.

15:52.890 --> 15:55.250
好  你们拍到了没?</br>
Okay, fellows, did you get that one?

15:55.260 --> 15:59.690
好了  参议员 麻烦你和柯里昂太太合照</br>
Now, Senator, just you and Mrs. Corleone.

16:00.630 --> 16:03.090
好了  那样就行了</br>
Okay that's enough, Senator

16:05.670 --> 16:07.320
请把支票给我</br>
Give me the cheque.

16:07.330 --> 16:10.500
拿高点让我们看得见</br>
higher,so we can see it.

16:20.570 --> 16:22.230
这是我的律师汤姆哈金</br>
My lawyer Tom Hagen.

16:22.240 --> 16:23.590
葛瑞参议员</br>
Senator Geary.

16:23.600 --> 16:26.740
是他负责和你的手下 安排这整件事</br>
He arranged everything through your man Turnbull.

16:26.850 --> 16:28.600
是的…</br>
Yes, yes.

16:28.610 --> 16:30.300
请坐</br>
Sit down.

16:33.210 --> 16:37.670
我以为我们两个要单独谈话</br>
Well I was under the impression that you and I would talk alone.

16:37.950 --> 16:40.740
这些人都是我的心腹  参议员</br>
I trust these men with my life, Senator.

16:41.220 --> 16:43.910
若是我要求他们离开 那就是侮辱他们</br>
To ask them to leave would be an insult.

16:43.920 --> 16:45.570
这个…</br>
Well,

16:45.580 --> 16:47.970
我是无所谓但是我得告诉你</br>
it's perfectly all right with me,

16:47.980 --> 16:49.310
我是个很直率的人</br>
but I am a blunt man

16:49.320 --> 16:51.940
而我预备很坦白的对你说</br>
and I intend to speak very frankly to you.

16:51.950 --> 16:57.520
也许比从前任何一位 你遇过的参议员都要坦白</br>
Maybe more frankly than anyone in my position has ever talked to you before.

16:57.590 --> 17:00.850
柯里昂家族在内华达 相当的成功</br>
The Corleone family has done well in Nevada.

17:00.860 --> 17:05.890
你拥有或者说控制了 拉斯维加斯的主要旅馆</br>
You own, or control, two major hotels in Vegas,

17:05.900 --> 17:07.720
在雷诺还有一家</br>
and one in Reno.

17:08.200 --> 17:10.790
执照是早就有的</br>
The licences were grandfathered in,

17:10.800 --> 17:15.190
所以在赌博委员会是没有问题</br>
so there was no problem with the Gaming Commission.

17:15.830 --> 17:18.960
现在我的消息来源告诉我</br>
Now my sources tell me

17:18.970 --> 17:22.290
你计划预备去动托比卡拉</br>
that you plan to make a move against the Tropigala.

17:23.000 --> 17:25.130
他们告诉我说在一周之内</br>
They tell me that, within a week,

17:25.140 --> 17:27.630
你就会把他们给扫地出门了</br>
you're going to move Klingman out.

17:28.110 --> 17:30.070
那是个不小的扩充</br>
Quite an expansion.

17:30.080 --> 17:34.400
不过你会遇到一个 技术上的问题</br>
However, it will leave you with a little technical problem.

17:36.610 --> 17:40.180
执照依然是克灵门的名字</br>
The licence will still be in Klingman's name.

17:40.680 --> 17:42.530
谭波是个好人</br>
Turnbull is a good man.

17:42.540 --> 17:45.470
好了  我们废话少说</br>
Yeah, well, let's cut out the bullshit.

17:45.480 --> 17:48.700
我不想在这里浪费许多时间</br>
I don't want to spend more time here than I have to.

17:48.710 --> 17:51.010
你可以拥有执照</br>
You can have the licence.

17:51.020 --> 17:54.040
代价是25万</br>
The price is 250,000 dollars.

17:54.050 --> 17:56.950
加上每个月总收入的5%</br>
Plus five per cent of the gross monthly,

17:56.960 --> 18:02.020
柯里昂先生 我是指四家旅馆合并的总收入</br>
of all four hotels, Mr. Corleone.

18:04.960 --> 18:09.180
现在执照的价格不超过二万元</br>
The price for the licence is less than 20,000 dollars,

18:09.190 --> 18:11.360
-我说的对不对? -没错</br>
-Am I right? -That's right.

18:12.270 --> 18:15.120
那我为何要付 这么高的价格呢?</br>
Why would I pay more than that?

18:15.130 --> 18:17.890
因为我意图要压迫你</br>
Because I intend to squeeze you.

18:18.060 --> 18:20.390
我不喜欢你这一类的人</br>
I don't like your kind of people.

18:20.700 --> 18:25.470
我不喜欢看到你油头粉面</br>
I don't like to see you come out to

18:25.470 --> 18:28.830
穿着那纯丝的西装</br>
this clean country in oily hair,dressed up in those silk suits

18:28.840 --> 18:32.570
假装是位正直的美国人</br>
and try to pass yourselves off as decent Americans.

18:32.740 --> 18:34.590
我是和你做生意</br>
I'll do business with you,

18:34.600 --> 18:38.840
但事实上我鄙视你的假面具</br>
but the fact is that I despise your masquerade,

18:38.850 --> 18:41.900
和你那种不择手段 向上爬的做事方式</br>
the dishonest way you pose yourself.

18:41.910 --> 18:44.580
你和你他妈的整个家族</br>
Yourself, and your whole fucking family.

18:51.810 --> 18:53.240
参议员</br>
Senator...

18:54.620 --> 18:57.390
我们两个都是伪善的人</br>
...we're both part of the same hypocrisy.

18:59.120 --> 19:03.010
但是永远也不要想 把我的家族拿来混为一谈</br>
But never think it applies to my family.

19:03.220 --> 19:09.760
好吧! 有些人就是喜欢玩点小把戏</br>
All right, all right.Some people have to play little games.

19:09.790 --> 19:11.490
你玩你的</br>
You play yours.

19:13.960 --> 19:15.220
让我们这样说好了!</br>
Let's say that

19:15.230 --> 19:18.520
你是为了自己本身的利益 而付钱给我</br>
you'll pay me because it's in your interest.

19:18.630 --> 19:21.790
明天中午前我要你的答覆和钱</br>
I want your answer and the money by noon tomorrow.

19:21.800 --> 19:26.540
还有一件事你不要再连络我了 永远不要</br>
One more thing.Don't you contact me again,ever.

19:26.570 --> 19:29.770
从今以后  你与罪犯去打交道</br>
From now on you deal with Turnbull.

19:29.770 --> 19:32.730
-开门!小子 -参议员</br>
-Open that door, son. -Senator,

19:33.000 --> 19:36.000
想的话  我现在就能答覆你</br>
you can have my answer now if you like.

19:37.610 --> 19:39.900
我要提供的是这个</br>
My offer is this:

19:40.470 --> 19:42.300
什么都没有</br>
Nothing.

19:43.780 --> 19:46.060
甚至不付赌博执照的费用</br>
Not even the fee for the gaming licence

19:46.070 --> 19:50.180
如果你个人能提供那项费用 我会很感激的</br>
which I would like you to put up personally.

19:54.740 --> 19:56.880
各位午安!</br>
Good afternoon, gentlemen.

19:59.880 --> 20:02.570
女士们  我不知道你们在外面</br>
Ladies! I didn't know you were out here.

20:02.580 --> 20:04.340
亲爱的  我们必须走了 我们已经迟了30分钟了</br>
Honey, we have to go. We're 30 minutes late.

20:04.350 --> 20:05.400
真的  真遗憾</br>
Really? I'm sorry.

20:05.410 --> 20:08.010
柯里昂太太  真是个好派对 谢谢你</br>
It's been delightful.

20:08.020 --> 20:10.150
那是我们的荣幸  非常感谢</br>
It was our pleasure.

20:10.160 --> 20:11.980
和你谈话真是愉快</br>
It was wonderful talking to you.

20:56.470 --> 20:57.630
弗雷多</br>
Fredo!

20:57.640 --> 21:00.740
弗雷多  你这个臭小子</br>
Fredo, you son-of-a-bitch,

21:00.750 --> 21:01.910
你气色看来真好</br>
