32:19.220 --> 32:21.610
令尊和海门罗斯做过生意</br>
Your father did business with Hyman Roth,

32:21.620 --> 32:24.140
令尊尊重海门罗斯</br>
he respected Hyman Roth,

32:24.150 --> 32:27.110
但他从来不信任海门罗斯</br>
but he never trusted Hyman Roth

32:27.120 --> 32:30.140
或是他的西西里人信差 强尼欧拉</br>
or his Sicilian messenger boy Johnny Ola.

32:30.150 --> 32:37.520
对不起  我先告退了 我有点累  又有点醉了</br>
You'll have to excuse me. I'm tired, and I'm a little drunk!

32:38.390 --> 32:40.950
而且我要这的每一位都知道</br>
I want everybody here to know,

32:40.960 --> 32:43.980
我不会为各位添任何的麻烦</br>
there's not going to be no trouble from me!

32:43.990 --> 32:45.990
柯里昂阁下</br>
Don Corleone.

32:46.100 --> 32:48.620
奇契  开门</br>
Cicci, the door...

32:56.370 --> 32:58.190
你要他们现在离开吗?</br>
You want him to leave now?

33:01.040 --> 33:02.830
让他们回纽约去吧</br>
Let him go back to New York.

33:02.840 --> 33:04.730
我已经拟好我的计划了</br>
I've already made my plans.

33:06.400 --> 33:09.010
那老头酒喝的太多了</br>
The old man had too much wine.

33:13.540 --> 33:15.100
时候不早了</br>
It's late.

33:27.490 --> 33:28.870
胎儿好吗?</br>
How's the baby?

33:29.580 --> 33:31.510
在我体内睡着了</br>
Sleeping inside me.

33:32.550 --> 33:34.010
你觉得是个男孩吗?</br>
Does it feel like a boy?

33:34.020 --> 33:37.190
是的  是个男孩  麦克</br>
Yes, it does, Michael.

33:39.490 --> 33:40.850
凯</br>
Kay?

33:41.450 --> 33:43.880
我很抱歉今天这些人来</br>
I'm sorry about all the people today.

33:44.090 --> 33:48.020
时机不对 但是我也无能为力</br>
Bad timing.It couldn't be helped, though.

33:48.330 --> 33:51.320
它让我想到你以前告诉过我</br>
It made me think of what you once told me.

33:53.670 --> 33:57.980
五年内柯里昂家族事业 完全合法化</br>
"In five years the Corleone family will be completely legitimate."

33:57.990 --> 34:00.600
那是七年前的事了</br>
That was seven years ago.

34:03.270 --> 34:04.930
我知道</br>
I know.

34:05.470 --> 34:08.390
我在尽力  亲爱的</br>
I'm trying, darling.

34:58.800 --> 35:02.830
(你喜欢吗?爸爸)</br>
"Do you like it"

35:10.900 --> 35:12.560
你看过这个了吗?</br>
Did you see this?

35:27.470 --> 35:29.740
麦克  窗帘为何是开着的?</br>
Michael,why are the drapes open?

35:57.120 --> 35:59.110
-凯  你还好吗? -我还好</br>
Kay, are you all right?

35:59.120 --> 36:01.080
-你有没有中弹? -没有</br>
- Are you hit? - No.

36:03.860 --> 36:05.850
过去了!…</br>
It's over It's over.

36:08.190 --> 36:10.520
把门关起来!</br>
Get the door locked!

36:11.500 --> 36:13.890
停住!…</br>
Stop,stop...

36:24.200 --> 36:25.630
他们还在这里面</br>
They're still on the property.

36:25.640 --> 36:27.930
拜托!麦克!拜托你留在里面</br>
Please stay inside.

36:27.940 --> 36:29.060
要活口</br>
Keep them alive.

36:29.070 --> 36:32.140
-我们尽力 -罗可!抓活口</br>
- We'll try.-Alive!

36:33.110 --> 36:34.780
留在门口</br>
Stay by the door.

36:38.880 --> 36:41.940
留在房子附近</br>
Stay around house.

37:54.810 --> 37:56.340
进来</br>
Yeah, come in.

38:03.650 --> 38:05.170
麦克  你还好吗?</br>
Mike, are you all right?

38:05.180 --> 38:07.180
-没事 -很好</br>
- Yeah.

38:10.730 --> 38:12.960
有许多事我不能告诉你</br>
Yeah,there's a lot I can't tell you.

38:15.230 --> 38:17.150
我知道过去你因此而很颓丧</br>
and I now that's upset you in the past.

38:17.160 --> 38:18.890
是有点儿</br>
A little.

38:19.730 --> 38:23.750
你觉得那表示缺少信任与信心</br>
You felt it was because of some lack of trust or confidence.

38:25.070 --> 38:26.590
但那是…</br>
But it's...

38:26.600 --> 38:30.130
是因为我钦佩你而且我爱你</br>
because I admire you and love you,

38:30.140 --> 38:32.900
所以我才对你保守秘密</br>
that I kept things secret from you.

38:34.640 --> 38:39.030
也因此在这个时候 你是我唯一能信任的人</br>
Now you're the only one I can trust.

38:40.510 --> 38:42.240
弗雷多?</br>
Fredo?

38:42.440 --> 38:44.670
他有个善良的心</br>
Well, he's got a good heart.

38:44.900 --> 38:47.530
但是他很懦弱而且很笨</br>
But he's weak and he's stupid

38:47.540 --> 38:50.280
而这是生死攸关的事</br>
nd this is life and death.

38:50.450 --> 38:54.100
汤姆!你是我的兄弟</br>
Tom, you're my brother.

38:59.490 --> 39:05.080
我一直希望你把我当成你兄弟 像亲兄弟一样</br>
I always wanted to be thought of as a brother by you, Mikey. A real brother.

39:07.160 --> 39:08.950
我知道</br>
I know that.

39:15.390 --> 39:17.420
你要接管一切</br>
You're going to take over.

39:18.420 --> 39:20.210
你将成为族长!</br>
You're going to be the Don.

39:23.590 --> 39:26.520
若是发生的事和我想的一样</br>
If what I think has happened,

39:26.930 --> 39:29.090
我今晚就要离开这里</br>
I'm leaving here tonight.

39:29.960 --> 39:31.920
我给予你完全的权力</br>
I give you complete power.

39:31.930 --> 39:36.360
包括弗雷多及他的手下 还有罗可  纳利所有人</br>
Over Fredo and his men. Rocco, Neri, everyone.

39:37.740 --> 39:41.270
我把我太太的性命交付给你</br>
I'm trusting you with the lives of my wife

39:41.300 --> 39:43.120
还有我的孩子</br>
and my children,

39:43.170 --> 39:45.090
以及这个家族的未来</br>
the future of this family.

39:48.000 --> 39:49.430
若是我们抓到这些傢伙</br>
If we catch them,

39:49.440 --> 39:51.660
你看有否可能查出 幕后主使者吗?</br>
will we find out...

39:51.670 --> 39:53.640
没必要去抓</br>
We won't catch them.

39:54.670 --> 39:55.960
除非我错的离谱</br>
Unless I'm very wrong,

39:55.970 --> 39:58.010
否则他们应该已经死了</br>
they're dead already.

39:59.720 --> 40:02.370
被一位很接近我们的人杀死</br>
They were killed by somebody close to us.

40:03.110 --> 40:04.740
是内奸</br>
Inside.

40:04.750 --> 40:08.240
非常怕会曝光</br>
Very,very frightened that they botched it.

40:08.250 --> 40:10.640
那么你的人呢?罗可和纳利</br>
You don't think that Rocco and Neri

40:10.650 --> 40:12.820
你不会认为他们与此事有关吧</br>
had something to do with this?

40:15.990 --> 40:17.510
你知道吗?</br>
See...

40:17.520 --> 40:20.760
我们的人都是生意人</br>
All our people are businessmen.

40:21.850 --> 40:24.750
他们的忠诚是以那个为基础</br>
Their loyalty is based on that.

40:27.250 --> 40:29.960
我由爸爸那里学到了一点</br>
One thing I learned from Pop...

40:31.270 --> 40:35.720
试着想想你身边的人 会怎么想?</br>
...was to try to think as people around you think.

40:36.700 --> 40:39.760
在生意的基础上 凡事都有可能</br>
On that basis, anything is possible.

40:41.560 --> 40:45.520
他们死在那里 就在我窗户外面</br>
Mike, they're dead! Right outside my window!

40:45.530 --> 40:48.890
我要离开这里  否则死的是我</br>
I want to get out of here.They're lying there dead!

40:48.900 --> 40:50.220
拉她进去!</br>
Get her in!

40:59.940 --> 41:02.900
在这边!他们有两个人</br>
Over here! There's two of them.

41:02.910 --> 41:04.640
看来像是由纽约以外的人雇的</br>
Looks like they were hired out of New York.

41:04.650 --> 41:06.610
我不认识他们</br>
I don't recognise them.

41:07.580 --> 41:09.070
现在问不出什么了</br>
Won't get anything out of them now.

41:09.080 --> 41:10.460
看…</br>
Look,look...

41:10.470 --> 41:12.370
把他们解决掉</br>
Fish them out.

41:37.200 --> 41:39.260
好了  把尸体料理掉</br>
Get rid of the bodies.

41:39.490 --> 41:40.820
麦克到哪去了?</br>
Where's Mike?

41:40.830 --> 41:42.390
罗可!</br>
Rocco.

42:12.580 --> 42:18.540
安东尼!没事了  睡吧!</br>
Anthony, everything is going to be all right. Try to sleep.

42:34.050 --> 42:36.290
喜欢你的派对吗?</br>
Did you like your party?

42:36.920 --> 42:40.450
-我收到很多礼物 -我知道</br>
- I got lots of presents.-I know.

42:40.990 --> 42:42.480
你喜欢它们吗?</br>
Did you like them?

42:42.530 --> 42:46.060
我不认得送我礼物的那些人</br>
Yeah. I didn't know the people who gave them to me.

42:47.000 --> 42:48.760
他们都是朋友</br>
Well, they were friends.

42:50.670 --> 42:53.020
你看到我送你的礼物了吗?</br>
Did you see my present for you?

42:53.030 --> 42:54.800
就放在我的枕头上</br>
It was on my pillow.

42:57.530 --> 42:58.720
安东尼</br>
Anthony.

42:58.730 --> 43:01.260
我明天一大早就要离开</br>
I'm going to be leaving very early tomorrow.

43:01.270 --> 43:06.030
-你会带我去吗? -不  我不行</br>
- Will you take me? - No, I can't, Anthony.

43:06.040 --> 43:08.160
是什么事你必须要走?</br>
Why do you have to go?

43:09.010 --> 43:11.100
是生意  我必须要去</br>
I have to do business.

43:11.740 --> 43:13.740
我能帮你忙</br>
I could help you.

43:18.350 --> 43:20.700
是的  有一天你会的</br>
I know. Some day you will.

43:21.580 --> 43:23.350
睡一会吧!</br>
Get some sleep.

43:45.590 --> 43:53.520
(1917年  纽约市 维多柯里昂)</br>

44:40.580 --> 44:43.780
她非常美  你必须见见她</br>
She's really beautiful.You've got to see her.

45:03.830 --> 45:08.900
你等着看她吧 言语无法形容她的美</br>
Wait till you see her. Words can't describe her.

45:17.500 --> 45:22.660
我离开了那普勒斯 离开了妈妈</br>
I left Naples. I left Mama.

45:22.670 --> 45:26.300
为了辛苦的漂泊</br>
For a no-good tramp!

45:26.310 --> 45:32.100
现在我来到美国的纽约了</br>
Now here I am in America, in New York.

45:32.780 --> 45:37.540
独自一人  想念我的妈妈</br>
Alone! Thinking of my mother.

45:38.610 --> 45:41.380
没有任何家中的消息</br>
Without news from home.

45:43.050 --> 45:44.510
进来</br>
Enter!

45:44.550 --> 45:47.410
有信</br>
Pepino, a letter for you!

45:47.820 --> 45:49.320
你坐下</br>
Have a seat.

45:49.520 --> 45:52.810
终于那普勒斯来信了</br>
Finally, a letter from Naples!

45:54.420 --> 45:57.990
维多  喜欢我的小天使吗?</br>
Vito, how do you like my little angel?

45:58.350 --> 46:00.650
美吧</br>
Isn't she beautiful?

46:00.660 --> 46:02.150
她是很美</br>
She's very beautiful.

46:02.160 --> 46:03.510
对你而言  她很美</br>
To you, she's beautiful.

46:03.520 --> 46:06.290
而我心中只有我的妻子小孩</br>
For me, there's only my wife and son.

46:06.490 --> 46:08.820
亲爱的妈妈</br>
And mama

46:10.390 --> 46:19.530
妈妈死了!妈妈…</br>
Our dear mother is dead!

47:07.490 --> 47:12.880
我们等会到后台去 带她去宵夜</br>
We'll go backstage later and take her to eat.

47:16.700 --> 47:21.870
你坐下  笨蛋</br>
Sit down, you bum!

47:25.160 --> 47:28.690
抱歉!范伦奇阁下</br>
Oh, excuse me, Don Fanucci.

47:35.440 --> 47:38.530
我们到后台去看她</br>
We'll go see her backstage.

47:40.700 --> 47:45.280
-那是谁? -黑手党</br>
-Who was that?-The Black Hand.

47:58.120 --> 48:01.780
维多  来吧!我们走</br>
Vito,come on...

48:01.790 --> 48:03.950
快点  我们到后台去看她</br>
Come on let's go see her backstage.

48:05.150 --> 48:08.050
借过!…</br>
Sorry,sorry...

48:12.750 --> 48:17.150
来这边</br>
Please.

48:17.220 --> 48:19.080
那是范伦奇  黑手党</br>
That's Fanucci... the Black Hand.

48:19.090 --> 48:22.480
我们明天再说吧</br>
We'll talk about it tomorrow.

48:23.030 --> 48:30.620
明天!永远是明天</br>
Tomorrow! Always tomorrow!

48:30.930 --> 48:37.830
你今天就要付钱</br>
You'll pay me today!

48:39.460 --> 48:40.830
我们走!</br>
Let's go.

48:41.400 --> 48:48.700
-快付钱 -别弄我女儿  放过她</br>
-Pay me now! -Not my daughter! Let her go!

48:48.710 --> 48:53.560
这!我所有的钱都给你</br>
Here, take all my money!

48:58.280 --> 49:01.020
维多…走吧</br>
Vito, come on.

49:03.880 --> 49:08.880
维多  我知道你怎么想</br>
I know what you're thinking.

49:08.890 --> 49:10.880
但事情不是那样的</br>
But you don't know how things are.

49:10.890 --> 49:12.610
范伦奇是黑手党</br>
Fanucci's with the Black Hand.

49:12.620 --> 49:15.050
这一带全都得付他钱</br>
The whole neighborhood pays him.

49:15.060 --> 49:17.140
即使是我开杂货店的爸爸</br>
Even my father, in the grocery store.

49:17.150 --> 49:18.380
他是意大利人?</br>
If he's Italian...

49:18.390 --> 49:20.640
他为何要骚扰 其他的意大利人?</br>
...why does he bother other Italians?

49:20.650 --> 49:22.920
他知道没别人保护他们</br>
He knows they have nobody to protect them.

49:22.930 --> 49:27.780
别管那个 喜欢我的小天使吗?</br>
Forget that. Did you like my angel?

49:27.790 --> 49:29.930
若是你快乐  我就快乐</br>
If you're happy, I'm happy.

50:17.820 --> 50:19.380
工作顺利吗</br>
Don't you feel well?

50:23.920 --> 50:26.350
你老板对你还好吗?</br>
Is your boss treating you all right?

50:27.420 --> 50:29.240
别提它了</br>
Forget it.

50:32.160 --> 50:33.790
隔壁的</br>
Hey! Paisan!

50:43.000 --> 50:45.020
你是意大利人吗?</br>
Hey, you speak Italian?

50:51.100 --> 50:56.060
帮我保管一下 下星期我再回来拿</br>
Hide this for me!Next week. I'll come and get it!

51:34.760 --> 51:40.390
阿班达多  见过我的侄子</br>
Abbandando, meet my nephew!

51:41.860 --> 51:44.990
生意好吗?</br>
How's business?

51:49.830 --> 51:53.150
很好!…</br>
It's good, it's good.

51:57.730 --> 52:02.800
范伦奇疯了! 说邻居在拖付钱的限期</br>
Fanucci's mad. Says the neighborhood's getting sloppy.

52:02.810 --> 52:07.470
说人们不准时付钱 不付全额的钱</br>
People don't pay on time, don't pay the full amount.

52:07.480 --> 52:10.170
说他对大家都太好了</br>
Says he's been too nice to everyone.

52:15.210 --> 52:17.570
所以范伦奇要改变了?</br>
So Fanucci's changing?

52:17.580 --> 52:20.800
当然  他想收双倍的钱</br>
Sure. He wants double from everybody.

52:20.810 --> 52:25.280
甚至我父亲也要付双倍</br>
Even from my father.

52:25.820 --> 52:27.680
我是你的朋友  对不对?</br>
I'm a friend, right?

52:27.690 --> 52:32.380
所以你会让他在这里做事</br>
So you'll let him work here?

52:45.390 --> 52:48.990
维多!过来一下</br>
Vito,come here.

52:57.630 --> 53:02.090
我有一个坏消息</br>
I've got some bad news.

53:04.210 --> 53:10.930
我实在不想告诉你这个…</br>
I feel rotten about telling you this...

53:10.940 --> 53:17.290
但范伦奇…他有位侄子 而你必须把我的工作给他</br>
But Fanucci... he's got a nephew...And you have to give him my job.

53:20.280 --> 53:25.270
你从我来这起 就一直对我很好</br>
You've always been good to me, ever since I came here.

53:25.280 --> 53:30.080
你像父亲般照顾我</br>
You looked after me like a father.

53:30.090 --> 53:38.380
我谢谢你  而且我不会忘记</br>
I thank you.And I won't forget it.

53:50.920 --> 53:52.310
维多</br>
Vito!

53:57.190 --> 53:58.960
不!…</br>
No...

53:59.500 --> 54:00.820
不!</br>
Oh, no!

54:00.830 --> 54:04.890
把这个带回去</br>
Take this to your family.

54:04.900 --> 54:07.050
谢谢你  但是我不能接受</br>
Thanks anyway. But please, I can't accept.

54:07.060 --> 54:11.420
-给你的家人 -我不能接受</br>
-Take this to your family. -I can't accept.

54:11.430 --> 54:13.140
不!</br>
No!

54:42.310 --> 54:44.780
好漂亮的梨子</br>
What a nice pear!

55:07.530 --> 55:11.060
我是克里曼沙 我的货还在你那</br>
I'm Clemenza, you still have my goods?

55:13.240 --> 55:15.970
你是否看过里面了?</br>
Did you look inside?

55:16.970 --> 55:20.500
我对于不关我事的 东西没兴趣</br>
I'm not interested in things that don't concern me.

55:30.980 --> 55:33.670
我的一位朋友有张很好的地氈</br>
A friend of mine has a nice rug.

55:33.680 --> 55:36.170
也许你太太会喜欢</br>
Maybe your wife would like it.

55:42.240 --> 55:45.810
她当然会  但谁有钱来买呢?</br>
Sure she would. But who has money for a rug?

55:45.820 --> 55:53.040
那是件礼物 我晓得如何回报的</br>
It would be a present. I know how to return a favor.

55:59.620 --> 56:04.410
当然好  我太太会喜欢它的</br>
Yeah,sure.My wife would like it.

56:07.630 --> 56:09.680
跟我来</br>
Let's go

56:27.900 --> 56:33.300
那王八蛋  他不在家</br>
The son of a bitch! He isn't home!

56:34.140 --> 56:37.470
该死!甚至连钥匙都没留下</br>
Damn, he didn't even leave the key.

56:41.170 --> 56:43.670
他不会介意的</br>
Well, he won't mind.

56:54.480 --> 56:59.210
你先请!维多!请进吧!</br>
Come on in. Hey,Vito come on in.

56:59.220 --> 57:02.150
别担心!进来吧!</br>
Please come on in.

57:22.330 --> 57:26.360
-这是你朋友的地方? -是的</br>
-This is your friend's place? -Yes.

57:26.800 --> 57:29.060
真像一座皇宫</br>
This is a real palace.

57:29.170 --> 57:31.200
最好的一座</br>
One of the best.

57:37.500 --> 57:40.230
维多!帮个忙  好吗?</br>
Vito, give me a hand, will you?

59:36.390 --> 59:39.560
看看那有多漂亮!尚尼</br>
Look how pretty it is, Santino!

01:02:08.590 --> 01:02:10.200
请进</br>
Come on in.

01:02:12.430 --> 01:02:15.950
没关系的  海门在里面</br>
It's all right. Hyman's in there.

01:02:15.960 --> 01:02:18.450
我只是在弄午餐 你要来一个鲔鱼三明治吗?</br>
Would you like a tuna sandwich?

01:02:18.460 --> 01:02:20.100
不  谢谢你</br>
No, thank you.

01:02:31.510 --> 01:02:33.000
罗斯先生?</br>
Mr. Roth?

01:02:33.580 --> 01:02:35.140
请进  麦克</br>
Come in, Michael.

01:02:36.940 --> 01:02:39.870
坐吧!像自己家一样</br>
Sit down, make yourself comfortable.

01:02:41.440 --> 01:02:43.610
球赛快结束了</br>
It's almost over.

01:02:45.520 --> 01:02:47.440
你看足球赛吗?</br>
Do you follow the football game?

01:02:48.920 --> 01:02:50.870
有一阵子没看了</br>
Not for a while I haven't.

01:02:50.890 --> 01:02:53.910
我喜欢在下午看足球赛</br>
I enjoy watching football in the afternoon.

01:02:53.920 --> 01:02:56.590
那是我喜爱这国家的诸事之一</br>
One of the things I love about this country.

01:02:56.790 --> 01:02:58.790
还有棒球</br>
Baseball too.

01:02:59.030 --> 01:03:03.780
从1919年阿诺罗斯坦 成立世界联盟以来</br>
Ever since Arnold Rothstein fixed the World Series in 1919.

01:03:03.790 --> 01:03:05.680
我就喜欢它了</br>

01:03:10.930 --> 01:03:13.160
我听说你遇到了麻烦</br>
I heard you had some trouble.

01:03:16.160 --> 01:03:18.060
太笨了</br>
Stupid.

01:03:19.060 --> 01:03:22.130
拿枪做出那种行为来</br>
People behaving like that with guns.

01:03:23.970 --> 01:03:26.200
重要的是你安然无恙</br>
The important thing is you're all right.

01:03:26.870 --> 01:03:30.860
拥有健康是最重要的事!</br>
Good health is the most important thing.

01:03:30.870 --> 01:03:34.030
比成功、金钱来的重要</br>
More than success, more than money.

01:03:35.410 --> 01:03:37.340
比权力更重要</br>
More than power.

01:03:51.550 --> 01:03:54.640
我来这是因为 将会有更多流血事件</br>
I came here because there's going to be more bloodshed.

01:03:55.520 --> 01:03:57.640
我要你在一切开始前先知晓</br>
I wanted you to know

01:03:57.650 --> 01:04:00.250
以免引发另一场战争</br>
so another war won't start.

01:04:00.550 --> 01:04:02.610
没有人希望有另一场战争</br>
Nobody wants another war.

01:04:03.620 --> 01:04:06.110
法兰克潘坦居利到我家里来</br>
Frank Pentangeli asked my permission

01:04:06.120 --> 01:04:09.550
而且他要求我的同意 除掉罗萨多兄弟</br>
to get rid of the Rosato brothers.

01:04:09.560 --> 01:04:11.970
当我拒绝时  他试图杀了我</br>
When I refused he tried to have me killed.

01:04:11.980 --> 01:04:13.610
他很笨  我运气很好</br>
He was stupid, I was lucky.

01:04:13.620 --> 01:04:15.320
我很快的会去拜访他</br>
I'll visit him soon.

01:04:15.500 --> 01:04:20.750
重要的是没有任何事 会妨碍我们对于未来的计划</br>
The important thing is that nothing interferes with ourplans for the future.

01:04:20.760 --> 01:04:23.620
你我意见相同 没有什么比那更重要</br>
Nothing is more important.

01:04:25.900 --> 01:04:28.950
你是个考虑周到的年轻人</br>
You're a wise and considerate man.

01:04:28.960 --> 01:04:31.200
而你是位伟人  罗斯先生</br>
And you're a great man, Mr. Roth.

01:04:31.930 --> 01:04:33.860
我还要向你学习很多</br>
There's much I can learn from you.

01:04:34.570 --> 01:04:37.060
只要我能帮的上忙  麦克</br>
Whatever I can do to help, Michael.

01:04:39.070 --> 01:04:41.970
-打扰了  午餐来了 -进来</br>
- Excuse me. Lunch. - Come in.

01:04:42.140 --> 01:04:43.790
谢谢你  亲爱的</br>
Thank you, my dear.

01:04:43.800 --> 01:04:46.970
你这干什么?会震破耳膜的</br>
You're going to break your eardrums.

01:04:47.710 --> 01:04:50.230
-慢慢享用吧! -谢谢你</br>
- Enjoy it. - Thank you.

01:04:55.920 --> 01:04:58.640
你还年轻  我老了  又有病</br>
You're young, I'm old and sick.

01:04:59.890 --> 01:05:04.880
我们在往后几个月所要做的事 可以创造历史</br>
What we'll do in the next few months will make history.

01:05:04.890 --> 01:05:07.750
那是破天荒的事</br>
It's never been done before.

01:05:07.760 --> 01:05:12.640
甚至令尊作梦也想不到 会有可能做到</br>
Not even your father would dream that such a thing could be possible.

01:05:14.320 --> 01:05:19.140
而法兰克潘坦居利该死 你没意见吧?</br>
Frank Pentangeli is a dead man. You don't object?

01:05:20.430 --> 01:05:22.580
他只是个小角色!</br>
He's small potatoes.

01:05:33.230 --> 01:05:34.790
什么事?</br>
What's up?

01:05:37.970 --> 01:05:40.060
我们有客人吗?</br>
We got company?

01:05:54.330 --> 01:05:59.920
-麦克柯里昂来了 -麦克柯里昂?</br>
-Michael Corleone is here. -Michael Corleone?

01:05:59.930 --> 01:06:04.730
他在你的房里  你最好快点</br>
He's in your den. You better hurry.

01:06:04.740 --> 01:06:07.060
他等了半个小时了</br>
He's been waiting a half hour.

01:06:13.680 --> 01:06:16.070
有什么不对了吗?</br>
Is something wrong?

01:06:19.930 --> 01:06:21.390
柯里昂阁下</br>
Don Corleone

01:06:21.400 --> 01:06:22.990
我希望你来之前 能先告知我一声</br>
I wish you would have let me know you were coming.

01:06:23.000 --> 01:06:25.520
好让我为你准备点什么</br>
I could have prepared something.

01:06:25.530 --> 01:06:28.130
我不想让你晓得我要来</br>
I didn't want you to know.

01:06:34.870 --> 01:06:36.560
你听说我家发生的事了吗?</br>
You heard what happened?

01:06:36.570 --> 01:06:38.160
麦克  我差点没吓死</br>
I almost died.

01:06:38.170 --> 01:06:41.030
-我们后来才松了一口气 -在我的家里</br>
-We were so relieved.-In my home!

01:06:43.870 --> 01:06:47.300
在我的卧室  而我太太睡在那</br>
In my bedroom where my wife sleeps!

01:06:49.610 --> 01:06:52.570
在我孩子玩玩具的地方</br>
Where my children come to play.

01:06:53.710 --> 01:06:55.710
在我的家</br>
In my home.

01:07:12.790 --> 01:07:15.740
我要你帮助我报复</br>
I want you to help me take my revenge.

01:07:15.750 --> 01:07:20.790
麦克  任何事都可以 我能做些什么?</br>
Michael, anything. What can I do?

01:07:22.730 --> 01:07:25.650
把和罗萨多兄弟间的 麻烦解决掉</br>
Settle these troubles with the Rosato brothers.

01:07:26.060 --> 01:07:27.820
麦克!我不明白!</br>
I don't understand. I don't...

01:07:27.830 --> 01:07:30.690
听我说  我没有你那种脑筋</br>
I don't have your brain

01:07:30.700 --> 01:07:32.060
去做那些大生意</br>
for big deals.

01:07:32.070 --> 01:07:33.660
但这是市井之事</br>
But this is a street thing.

01:07:33.670 --> 01:07:38.860
那个迈阿密的海门罗斯 他在支持那些王八蛋</br>
That Hyman Roth in Miami. He's backing up those sons-of-bitches.

01:07:38.870 --> 01:07:40.030
我知道他在支持</br>
I know he is.

01:07:40.040 --> 01:07:41.390
那么是为什么?</br>
Then why?

01:07:41.400 --> 01:07:44.510
为何你要求我与他们谈和? 麦克</br>
So why ask me to lay down to them?

01:07:49.450 --> 01:07:52.410
是海门罗斯叫人杀我的</br>
It was Hyman Roth that tried to have me killed.

01:07:54.620 --> 01:07:56.380
我知道是他</br>
I know it was him.

01:07:57.820 --> 01:07:59.940
老天爷!麦克</br>
Jesus Christ, Mike.

01:08:00.250 --> 01:08:03.680
老天爷!让我们干掉他们 去把他们全部都给做了</br>
Jesus Christ, let's get them all.

01:08:03.690 --> 01:08:05.510
趁我们还有力量之前 现在就去</br>
Now while we've got the muscle.

01:08:10.420 --> 01:08:13.490
这里以前是家父的书房</br>
This used to be my father's old study.

01:08:14.300 --> 01:08:16.060
现在变了</br>
It's changed.

01:08:17.630 --> 01:08:19.300
我还记得以前…</br>
I remember...

01:08:20.160 --> 01:08:22.160
在这有张大桌子</br>
there used to be a big desk here.

01:08:25.030 --> 01:08:29.900
当我还是孩子之时 在这附近玩耍都要很小声</br>
I remember when I was a kid. We had to be quiet when we played near here.

01:08:37.600 --> 01:08:41.630
我很高兴这幢房子 始终不曾落入陌生人的手里</br>
I was very happy that this house never went to strangers.

01:08:42.710 --> 01:08:46.970
先是克里曼沙接手  现在是你</br>
First Clemenza took it over. Now you.

01:08:48.380 --> 01:08:51.080
家父在这里教了我许多事情</br>
My father taught me many things here.

01:08:51.180 --> 01:08:53.080
就在这间房间里教我的</br>
He taught me in this room.

01:08:56.880 --> 01:09:00.570
他教我与朋友保持接近</br>
He taught me, "Keep your friends close,

01:09:00.580 --> 01:09:02.920
但是敌人要更接近</br>
but your enemies closer."

01:09:03.050 --> 01:09:06.550
现在若是海门罗斯看到 我出面协调这件事</br>
If Hyman Roth sees that I interceded in this

01:09:06.560 --> 01:09:08.950
帮了罗萨多兄弟的忙</br>
in the Rosato brothers' favour

01:09:09.330 --> 01:09:12.320
他会认为与我的关然依然良好</br>
he'll think his relationship with me is still good.

01:09:12.330 --> 01:09:15.560
-明白吗? -明白</br>
-Capide? -Capide.

01:09:15.700 --> 01:09:17.860
我就是要他那样想</br>
That's what I want him to think.

01:09:18.830 --> 01:09:20.860
我要他们完全的放松</br>
I want him relaxed

01:09:20.870 --> 01:09:23.660
对我们的友谊有绝对的信心</br>
and confident in our friendship.

01:09:23.670 --> 01:09:25.130
那我就能查出来</br>
Then I'll be able to find out

01:09:25.140 --> 01:09:28.060
我家族里的叛徒是谁?</br>
who the traitor in my family was.

01:09:56.580 --> 01:09:58.950
弗雷多!我是强尼</br>
Fredo, this is Johnny Ola

01:09:59.160 --> 01:10:02.010
强尼欧拉!我们需要帮忙</br>
We need some more help,Johnny

01:10:02.020 --> 01:10:03.620
强尼?</br>
Johnny?

01:10:04.120 --> 01:10:06.890
老天爷  是什么时候了?</br>
Jesus Christ, what the hell time is it?

01:10:07.300 --> 01:10:08.680
是谁?甜心</br>
Who's that, honey?

01:10:08.830 --> 01:10:10.320
听清楚  弗雷多</br>
Listen good, Fredo,

01:10:10.330 --> 01:10:12.120
你为何打电话到这里来?</br>
Why are you calling me?

01:10:12.130 --> 01:10:13.720
我不想和你谈</br>
I don't want to talk to you.

01:10:13.730 --> 01:10:18.290
潘坦居利和罗萨多兄弟要开会 他说他会遵守他们的协定</br>
Pentangeli is going to accept the Rosato brothers' deal

01:10:18.330 --> 01:10:20.920
-他会一个人来吗? -我什么都不知道</br>
- Will he come alone?-I don't know.

01:10:20.930 --> 01:10:22.630
你们使我陷的够深了</br>
You've got me in deep enough already.

01:10:22.640 --> 01:10:23.990
只是一起去</br>
Just go along,

01:10:24.000 --> 01:10:25.440
也许协谈会很顺利</br>
everything will be all right,

01:10:25.440 --> 01:10:28.330
弗雷多 潘坦居利说他愿意达成协议</br>
Fredo,Pentangeli says he's willing to make a deal

01:10:28.340 --> 01:10:32.730
我们只想知道他是否说真话 还是会带手下一起来</br>
All we want to know is if he's on the level, or if he'll bring his boys

01:10:32.740 --> 01:10:35.900
你们对我说谎 不要再打电话给我</br>
You lied to me. I don't want you to call me anymore.

01:10:35.910 --> 01:10:38.230
你弟弟不会查出我们交谈过</br>
Your brother won't find out we talked

01:10:38.240 --> 01:10:40.270
我不知道你在说些什么</br>
I don't know what you're talking about.

01:10:51.350 --> 01:10:52.910
是谁?</br>
Who was that?

01:10:53.050 --> 01:10:55.450
打错电话的</br>
Wrong number.

01:11:03.760 --> 01:11:05.410
等等  我这里没有任何人</br>
Frankie, I've got nobody here.

01:11:05.420 --> 01:11:06.650
在车上等  奇契</br>
Wait in the car, Cicc'.

01:11:06.660 --> 01:11:09.230
-法兰克 -没事的  奇契</br>
- Frankie. - That's okay, Cicc'.

01:11:16.460 --> 01:11:17.860
这是什么?</br>
What's this?

01:11:17.870 --> 01:11:20.190
那是我们新协议的幸运符</br>
A lucky C note for our new deal.

01:11:23.270 --> 01:11:26.100
路契  给我们倒杯酒</br>
Ritchie. Give us a taste.

01:11:30.240 --> 01:11:33.770
我们对于你的决定都很高兴 法兰克</br>
We were all real happy about your decision, Frankie.

01:11:34.240 --> 01:11:36.000
你不会后悔的</br>
You won't regret it.

01:11:36.010 --> 01:11:38.640
我不喜欢这个标识  罗萨多</br>
I don't like the C note, Rosato.

01:11:38.650 --> 01:11:41.080
我认为那是种侮辱</br>
I take that as an insult.

01:11:41.440 --> 01:11:44.370
麦克叫我向你说声好</br>
Michael Corleone says hello!

01:12:01.000 --> 01:12:04.160
快点  把那扇门关起来</br>
Close the door!

01:12:04.160 --> 01:12:05.650
前面有条子  怎么…</br>
Your friend the cop...

01:12:06.500 --> 01:12:09.170
路契  里面很暗</br>
Hey, Ritch. It's dark in here.

01:12:09.200 --> 01:12:10.790
你在营业中还是已休息?</br>
Are you open or closed?

01:12:10.800 --> 01:12:13.900
我只是进来整理一下</br>
I just came in to clean up a little, you know?

01:12:17.010 --> 01:12:18.730
什么事?</br>
What's the matter?

01:12:19.370 --> 01:12:20.890
地板上有东西吗?</br>
Is that something on the floor?

01:12:20.900 --> 01:12:24.860
不  别在这!… 安东尼  别在这!</br>
Carmine, not here! Anthony!

01:12:26.970 --> 01:12:29.830
你打开酒吧门 我就把你的脑袋给轰掉</br>
You open this bar and I'll blow your head in!

01:13:16.470 --> 01:13:18.630
弗雷多!看到你真好</br>
Freddy, it's good to see you.

01:13:21.410 --> 01:13:26.600
-他怎样了? -没事了  在后面</br>
- How is he? - He's okay. He's in the back.

01:13:29.810 --> 01:13:32.200
好了!女孩们!闪到一边去吧</br>
Girls, take a hike.

01:13:35.580 --> 01:13:37.580
在这里这间房里面</br>
In this room here.

01:13:40.220 --> 01:13:42.070
我要先跟他单独谈谈</br>
I want to talk to him alone first.

01:13:42.080 --> 01:13:43.580
别这样</br>
Come on.

01:13:52.530 --> 01:13:54.950
我以为我能帮助你  参议员</br>
I thought I could help you, Senator.

01:13:59.160 --> 01:14:00.730
哈金?</br>
Hagen?

01:14:02.320 --> 01:14:04.560
哈金  我没有…</br>
Listen, I did not...

01:14:04.570 --> 01:14:06.590
没事了</br>
It's all right.

01:14:06.600 --> 01:14:07.920
我什么都没有做</br>
I didn't do anything.

01:14:07.930 --> 01:14:09.490
好的</br>
It's okay.

01:14:10.070 --> 01:14:11.960
你的运气很好</br>
You're very lucky.

01:14:12.270 --> 01:14:14.890
我弟弟弗雷多管理这个地方</br>
My brother Fredo operates this place.

01:14:14.900 --> 01:14:17.070
他们最先通知他</br>
He was called before anyone.

01:14:17.870 --> 01:14:19.230
这若发生在别的地方</br>
Had this happened some place else

01:14:19.240 --> 01:14:20.970
我们也帮不了你</br>
we couldn't have helped you.

01:14:24.670 --> 01:14:27.410
当我醒来时  我在地板上</br>
When I woke up, I was on the floor.

01:14:29.310 --> 01:14:31.370
而且我不知道那是怎么发生的</br>
And I don't know how it happened.

01:14:31.380 --> 01:14:33.170
你记不起来了?</br>
You can't remember?

01:14:37.110 --> 01:14:39.110
我昏了</br>
I passed out.

01:14:43.590 --> 01:14:47.940
我…我来整理!</br>

01:14:55.460 --> 01:14:57.310
只是一场游戏</br>
Just a game. Jesus.

01:14:57.320 --> 01:15:02.360
老天爷</br>
Jesus, Jesus!

01:15:08.800 --> 01:15:12.130
主!…</br>
Jesus God!

01:15:15.670 --> 01:15:17.130
若是有上帝的话…</br>
Oh God!

01:15:22.410 --> 01:15:25.370
我不知道 而且我不了解为什么</br>
I don't know, and I don't understand why

01:15:25.380 --> 01:15:26.540
我记不起来了</br>
I can't remember.

01:15:26.550 --> 01:15:29.440
你不需要记得 只要照我说的做</br>
Doesn't matter, just do as I say.

01:15:29.450 --> 01:15:31.910
打个电话到你的办公室去</br>
Put in a call to your office.

01:15:31.920 --> 01:15:33.240
解释一下</br>
Explain that

01:15:33.250 --> 01:15:35.880
说你明天下午会到</br>
you'll be there tomorrow.

01:15:36.020 --> 01:15:42.780
你决定在达荷的 麦克柯里昂家里住一晚</br>
You decided to spend the night at Michael Corleone's house in Tahoe.

01:15:42.790 --> 01:15:46.210
我记得她在笑</br>
I do remember that she was laughing.

01:15:47.650 --> 01:15:49.390
我们以前也玩过</br>
We'd done it before

01:15:49.660 --> 01:15:53.790
我知道我不可能伤害那个女孩</br>
and I know that I could not have hurt that girl.

01:15:54.160 --> 01:15:56.020
那个女孩没有家人</br>
This girl has no family.

01:15:56.030 --> 01:15:58.720
没有人知道她在这里工作</br>
Nobody knows that she worked here.

01:15:58.730 --> 01:16:01.260
等清理完毕  就不会有事了</br>
It'll be as though she never existed.

01:16:03.570 --> 01:16:05.860
那全是因为我们之间的友谊</br>
All that's left is our friendship.

01:16:21.250 --> 01:16:22.430
什么事?</br>
Yes?

01:16:22.440 --> 01:16:25.440
抱歉  柯里昂太太 我们奉命不能让你过去</br>
Sorry, but we're not to let you through.

01:16:26.010 --> 01:16:27.740
我只是要去市场</br>
I'm just going to the market.

01:16:27.750 --> 01:16:30.300
你只要把单子给我们 我们会为你买回来</br>
We'll pick up anything you want.

01:16:30.310 --> 01:16:31.740
这是谁的命令?</br>
Whose orders are these?

01:16:31.750 --> 01:16:33.640
哈金先生的  他正在途中</br>
Mr. Hagen's. He's coming.

01:16:33.650 --> 01:16:36.620
好的  那我得和哈金先生谈谈</br>
I'll speak to him.

01:16:41.890 --> 01:16:45.750
我本来早要跟你解释 但我在达荷市有些事要办</br>
I wanted to explain, but I had business in Carson City.

01:16:45.760 --> 01:16:47.950
这是顾忌你的安全 麦克的要求</br>
It's Michael's request for your safety.

01:16:47.960 --> 01:16:50.050
我们可以去为你买你所需要的</br>
We'll get anything you need.

01:16:50.060 --> 01:16:52.690
太好了  我被软禁在我的屋里</br>
So I'm supposed to stay in my house?

01:16:52.700 --> 01:16:55.130
不  在整座庭园中都可以活动</br>
No, within the compound will be fine.

01:16:55.160 --> 01:16:57.620
汤姆 我下周要带孩子们去新英格兰</br>
We were going to New England.

01:16:57.630 --> 01:16:59.150
取消了</br>
That's off.

01:16:59.160 --> 01:17:01.090
我是个囚犯  是不是?</br>
Am I a prisoner?

01:17:01.100 --> 01:17:02.590
我们不是那样认为  凯</br>
That's not how we see it, Kay.

01:17:02.600 --> 01:17:05.560
好吧!孩子们 来  我们回房去</br>
Come on, kids. We're going back to the house.

01:17:07.910 --> 01:17:09.360
乔!</br>
Joe.

01:17:55.570 --> 01:17:58.330
古巴!…</br>
Cuba, Cuba!

01:18:38.230 --> 01:18:40.110
各位贵宾</br>
Most respected gentlemen.

01:18:41.430 --> 01:18:43.850
欢迎你们光临哈瓦那市</br>
Welcome to Havana.

01:18:45.690 --> 01:18:50.930
我要谢谢这批著名的 美国工业家</br>
I want to thank this distinguished group of

01:18:52.740 --> 01:18:55.120
继续和古巴一起合作</br>
American industrialists for continuing to work with Cuba

01:18:56.440 --> 01:18:58.860
在她整个历史中</br>
for the greatest period of prosperity

01:19:00.530 --> 01:19:02.200
最光荣的一段时代里</br>
in her entire history.

01:19:03.530 --> 01:19:05.000
威廉萧先生</br>
Mr. William Shaw

01:19:05.880 --> 01:19:07.900
代表通用食品公司</br>
representing the General Fruit Company.

01:19:09.610 --> 01:19:11.640
康德先生和唐丹先生</br>
Messrs Corngold and Dant

01:19:12.410 --> 01:19:14.740
代表美国电话电报公司</br>
of United Telephone and Telegraph Company.

01:19:16.580 --> 01:19:18.140
派帝先生</br>
Mr. Petty

01:19:18.180 --> 01:19:22.100
是泛美矿业公司的地区副总裁</br>
regional Vice President of the Pan American Mining Corporation.

01:19:24.060 --> 01:19:26.880
罗勃特艾伦先生 南美糖业公司</br>
Mr. Robert Allen of South American Sugar.

01:19:28.450 --> 01:19:31.380
麦克柯里昂先生 来自内华达州</br>
Mr. Michael Corleone of Nevada.

01:19:32.620 --> 01:19:36.650
代表了我们 观光休闲活动事业的联盟</br>
representing our associates in tourism and leisure activities.

01:19:37.290 --> 01:19:40.690
还有我的老朋友及合伙人</br>
And my old friend and associate from Florida.

01:19:42.360 --> 01:19:44.360
来自佛罗里达的海门罗斯先生</br>
Mr. Hyman Roth.

01:19:44.630 --> 01:19:46.590
我要利用这个机会</br>
I would like to thank

01:19:46.600 --> 01:19:48.990
谢谢美国电话电报公司</br>
United Telephone and Telegraph

01:19:49.000 --> 01:19:50.390
所赠送的可爱的圣诞礼物</br>
for their Christmas gift.

01:19:55.170 --> 01:19:57.440
一座纯金的电话!</br>
A solid gold telephone.

01:19:59.940 --> 01:20:01.900
也许各位想要看看</br>
Perhaps you gentlemen would like to look at it.

01:20:04.170 --> 01:20:05.970
-总统先生 -什么事?</br>
- Mr. President? - Yes?

01:20:05.980 --> 01:20:09.860
也许你能谈谈叛乱的情况</br>
Could you discuss the rebel activity

01:20:09.870 --> 01:20:12.200
这对于我们的 生意会有何影响?</br>
and what this can mean to our businesses?

01:20:12.210 --> 01:20:13.600
-当然! -好重</br>
- Of course. - Heavy stuff.

01:20:13.610 --> 01:20:15.070
我要向各位保证</br>
I assure you that

01:20:15.120 --> 01:20:16.970
虽然叛乱分子在拉斯维拉</br>
lthough the rebels have started

01:20:16.980 --> 01:20:19.720
掀起惊人的动乱</br>
a campaign in Las Villas

01:20:25.650 --> 01:20:28.210
我的参谋们告诉我</br>
my staff indicates, with assurance

01:20:28.220 --> 01:20:33.080
我们能在新年之前将他们 赶出圣克拉拉</br>
that we'll drive them out of Santa Clara before the New Year.

01:20:35.690 --> 01:20:37.660
而且我希望你们能放心</br>
I want to put you all at ease.

01:20:38.360 --> 01:20:42.650
我们绝不容许游击队 出现在赌场或游泳池</br>
We will tolerate no guerrillas in the casinos or the swimming pools.

01:21:01.240 --> 01:21:03.200
他说他们在逮捕人</br>
He said that they're making an arrest

01:21:03.210 --> 01:21:06.040
几分钟后会让我们通过</br>
and in a few minutes he'll let us through.

01:21:06.480 --> 01:21:08.740
-强尼 -没什么</br>
-Johnny.-It's nothing.

01:21:08.750 --> 01:21:12.710
只是一群盗匪 警察在肃清他们</br>
Just some lousy bandits.The police are cleaning them up.

01:21:26.550 --> 01:21:28.110
你的蛋糕来了</br>
Viva Fidel!

01:21:31.990 --> 01:21:34.080
希望我的年龄没弄错</br>
I hope my age is correct.

01:21:34.100 --> 01:21:36.880
我对我的年龄一向很确定</br>
I'm always accurate about my age.

01:21:38.000 --> 01:21:41.690
在切蛋糕之前 让大家都看看蛋糕</br>
Make sure that everybody sees the cake before we cut it.

01:21:44.830 --> 01:21:46.790
我非常的高兴</br>
I'm very pleased

01:21:47.500 --> 01:21:52.460
你们从各地方前来 与我在这里相聚</br>
you're all able to come from such distances to be with me today.

01:21:53.700 --> 01:21:56.970
当一个人到了 他生命中的这一刻</br>
When a man comes to this point in his life

01:21:57.980 --> 01:22:01.570
他希望能将他被祝福的事 交付出去</br>
he wants to turn over the things he's been blessed with.

01:22:01.610 --> 01:22:03.560
把它们交给朋友</br>
Turn them over to friends

01:22:03.570 --> 01:22:07.180
像是给他所有的 朋友一种补偿</br>
as a reward for the friends he's had.

01:22:07.780 --> 01:22:11.410
也是要确定在他死了之后</br>
and to make sure that

01:22:11.420 --> 01:22:13.200
一切事情都还能够顺利进行</br>
everything goes well after he's gone.

01:22:13.210 --> 01:22:14.710
那还得等上很多年</br>
Not for years.

01:22:16.090 --> 01:22:18.640
我们会知道的  医生们不同意</br>
We'll see. The doctors would disagree

01:22:18.650 --> 01:22:20.380
但他们又晓得什么?</br>
but what do they know?

01:22:21.460 --> 01:22:26.680
我们在哈瓦那 所达成的美好成就</br>
These are wonderful things that we've achieved in Havana

01:22:26.690 --> 01:22:29.650
由此开始毫无止境</br>
and there's no limit to where we can go from here.

01:22:29.660 --> 01:22:34.420
这种政府了解如何协助企业 如何去鼓励…</br>
This kind of government knows how to help business,to encourage it.

01:22:34.430 --> 01:22:38.650
这里的旅馆事业 和我们在拉斯维加斯</br>
The hotels here are bigger and swankier than

01:22:38.660 --> 01:22:41.660
任何粗鄙的场所 都要更大、更豪华</br>
any of the joints in Vegas.

01:22:41.670 --> 01:22:44.760
我们要谢谢在古巴政府的友人</br>
We can thank our friends in the Cuban government

01:22:44.770 --> 01:22:49.530
在平等的基础上 放宽了进口的限制</br>
which has put up half the cash with the Teamsters,on a dollar for dollar basis

01:22:49.540 --> 01:22:52.460
而且只需先付一半的现金</br>
and has relaxed restrictions on imports.

01:22:52.470 --> 01:22:53.600
我要说的是</br>
What I'm saying is

01:22:53.610 --> 01:22:56.830
我们有了我们所需要的</br>
that we have now what we have always needed:

01:22:56.840 --> 01:22:59.740
与政府的真正合伙关系</br>
Real partnership with a government.

01:22:59.870 --> 01:23:01.440
小块一点</br>
Smaller piece.

01:23:02.570 --> 01:23:05.300
你们全都认得麦克柯里昂</br>
You all know Michael Corleone

01:23:05.310 --> 01:23:07.500
而且我们全都记得他的父亲</br>
and we all remember his father.

01:23:07.510 --> 01:23:11.340
在我退休或死亡的时候</br>
At the time of my retirement, or death

01:23:11.350 --> 01:23:15.810
我把我整个哈瓦那所有的企业</br>
I turn over all my interests in the Havana operation

01:23:15.820 --> 01:23:17.340
全移转给他管理</br>
to his control.

01:23:17.350 --> 01:23:19.250
但是…</br>
But

01:23:19.390 --> 01:23:21.850
你们全部都会有一份</br>
all of you will share.

01:23:21.860 --> 01:23:25.320
纳西翁雷归湖村路兄弟管理</br>
The Nacionale will go to the Lakeville Road Boys

01:23:25.330 --> 01:23:28.650
卡普利归柯里昂家族</br>
the Capri to the Corleone family

01:23:28.660 --> 01:23:31.150
塞维拉毕特摩也是</br>
the Sevilla Biltmore also

01:23:31.160 --> 01:23:34.820
但新港的艾迪拉文 将引进潘尼诺兄弟</br>
but Eddie Levine will bring in the Pennino brothers

01:23:34.830 --> 01:23:37.760
尼诺和艾迪得一部分的主权</br>
Dino and Eddie, for a piece

01:23:37.770 --> 01:23:39.990
和实际赌场经营的管理权</br>
and to handle the casino operations.

01:23:40.000 --> 01:23:43.720
而且还保留一部分 给内华达的朋友</br>
We've saved a piece for some friends in Nevada

01:23:43.730 --> 01:23:46.970
以确定家乡的事都能够顺利</br>
to make sure that things go smoothly back home.

01:23:49.470 --> 01:23:52.470
希望大家好好享用蛋糕</br>
I want all of you to enjoy your cake.

01:23:52.480 --> 01:23:54.670
所以…吃吧!</br>
So, enjoy!

01:23:54.680 --> 01:23:55.970
生日快乐</br>
Happy birthday!

01:23:58.480 --> 01:24:01.070
我今天看到一件有趣的事</br>
I saw an interesting thing happen today.

01:24:02.210 --> 01:24:05.540
一个叛党被宪兵逮捕了</br>
A rebel was being arrested by the military police.

01:24:05.550 --> 01:24:10.170
他不但不肯被生擒 还引爆身上的手榴弹</br>
Rather than be taken alive, he exploded a grenade he had in his jacket.

01:24:10.180 --> 01:24:13.610
他自杀了 还连带炸死一位指挥的队长</br>
He killed himself and took a captain of the command with him.

01:24:13.620 --> 01:24:16.550
-对吧?强尼 -那些叛党  他们是神经病</br>
-Right,Johnny?-Those rebels are lunatics.

01:24:16.790 --> 01:24:22.740
也许如此  不过这使我想到 军人是拿薪水作战</br>
Maybe so.But it occurred to me,that the soldiers are paidto fight

01:24:22.750 --> 01:24:24.290
叛党则不是</br>
the rebels aren't.

01:24:24.300 --> 01:24:26.120
那告诉了你什么?</br>
What does that tell you?

01:24:26.660 --> 01:24:28.390
他们可能会赢!</br>
They can win.

01:24:30.360 --> 01:24:33.220
这国家过去50年来都有叛乱</br>
This country has had rebels for 50 years.

01:24:33.230 --> 01:24:35.080
他们的天性就是如此 相信我  我知道</br>
It's in their blood.I know.

01:24:35.090 --> 01:24:37.670
我由20年代就开始来这里了</br>
I've been coming here since the Twenties.

01:24:37.970 --> 01:24:39.720
当你还是婴儿时</br>
We were running molasses from Havana

01:24:39.730 --> 01:24:41.550
我们就在这经营哈瓦那的糖业</br>
when you were a baby.

01:24:41.870 --> 01:24:44.800
那卡车是令尊所有的</br>
The trucks were owned by your father.

01:24:45.510 --> 01:24:47.170
麦克</br>
Mikey.

01:24:54.210 --> 01:24:57.270
我宁愿我们单独相处时 才讨论这事</br>
I'd rather we talked about this when we're alone.

01:24:59.980 --> 01:25:02.880
那二百万一直没来到岛上</br>
The two million never got to the island.

01:25:08.790 --> 01:25:12.340
我不希望话传出去说 你因担心叛乱…</br>
It mustn't be known that you held back the money

01:25:12.350 --> 01:25:15.020
而不肯把钱拿出来</br>
because you worried about the rebels.

01:25:21.160 --> 01:25:25.450
坐下…</br>
Sit down, Michael. Sit down.

01:25:32.370 --> 01:25:36.820
我若能活到看见 和你一起达到顶峰就好了</br>
If I could only live to see it, to be there with you.

01:25:38.570 --> 01:25:43.700
我愿用一切来换取20年的寿命</br>
What I wouldn't give for 20 more years.

01:25:44.540 --> 01:25:47.130
我们在这里被保护着</br>
Here we are, protected.

01:25:47.140 --> 01:25:49.500
能自由的争取我们的利润</br>
Free to make our profits without Kefauver

01:25:49.510 --> 01:25:53.230
而不被司法部及调查局打扰</br>
the goddamn Justice Department and the FBI .

01:25:53.240 --> 01:25:54.870
身在90哩之外</br>
90 miles away

01:25:54.880 --> 01:25:57.470
与友善的政府合伙</br>
in partnership with a friendly government.

01:25:58.120 --> 01:26:02.210
也许有些小事情  但不算什么</br>
90 miles. It's nothing.

01:26:02.520 --> 01:26:05.650
对一个想成为美国总统的人</br>
Just one small step for a man looking to

01:26:05.660 --> 01:26:08.410
这只是小小的一步罢了</br>
be President of the United States

01:26:08.420 --> 01:26:11.520
又有足够的金钱让它成为可能</br>
and having the cash to make it possible.

01:26:11.860 --> 01:26:13.310
麦克!</br>
Mikey!

01:26:15.060 --> 01:26:17.220
我们比美国钢铁公司还要大</br>
we're bigger than U.S. Steel.

01:26:44.410 --> 01:26:47.370
麦克!你好吗?</br>
Mikey, how are you? Okay?

01:26:48.680 --> 01:26:51.500
我是弗雷多柯里昂</br>
Hi! Freddie Corleone.

01:26:51.770 --> 01:26:53.480
是我哥哥</br>
Mio frati

01:26:54.780 --> 01:26:57.070
老天爷!这一路真辛苦</br>
Jesus Christ, what a trip!

01:26:57.080 --> 01:26:58.240
一路上我都在想万一有人知道</br>
I thought, "What if somebody knows

01:26:58.250 --> 01:27:00.450
我这里面装了什么</br>
what I've got in here".

01:27:00.610 --> 01:27:01.840
你能想像吗?</br>
Can you imagine that?

01:27:01.850 --> 01:27:05.450
二百万元在飞机座位旁</br>
Two million dollars on the seat next to me.

01:27:09.280 --> 01:27:11.890
-对不起 -没关系的</br>
- Excuse me. - It's okay.

01:27:13.390 --> 01:27:15.060
你要数数看吗?</br>
You want to count it?

01:27:19.890 --> 01:27:21.990
麦克  这里究竟是怎么回事</br>
What's going on?

01:27:22.260 --> 01:27:23.490
我完全蒙在鼓里</br>
I'm totally in the dark.

01:27:23.500 --> 01:27:25.660
家族在哈瓦那要进行投资</br>
The family is making an investment in Havana.

01:27:25.670 --> 01:27:27.870
这些是给总统的礼物</br>
This is a gift for the President.

01:27:29.070 --> 01:27:32.860
那太好了  哈瓦那好极了</br>
That's great! Havana's great.

01:27:34.240 --> 01:27:36.270
是我这种人的城市</br>
It's my kind of town.

01:27:37.570 --> 01:27:39.570
有我认识的人在哈瓦那吗?</br>
Anybody I know in Havana?

01:27:39.680 --> 01:27:42.770
我不知道  有海门罗斯 强尼欧拉</br>
Don't know. Hyman Roth, Johnny Ola?

01:27:45.350 --> 01:27:48.910
不认得  我从未见过他们</br>
No. I've never met them.

01:27:51.650 --> 01:27:54.080
听我说  麦克  我…</br>
Listen, Mikey, I'm kind of...

01:27:54.220 --> 01:27:55.910
我有点…</br>
...kind of

01:27:59.550 --> 01:28:01.240
这一路上让我有点紧张</br>
nervous from the trip.

01:28:01.250 --> 01:28:04.650
我能…喝杯酒吗?</br>
Can I get a drink or something?

01:28:04.720 --> 01:28:07.490
我想也许我们可以一起出去</br>
I thought maybe we'd go out together.

01:28:07.950 --> 01:28:11.620
我知道一个好地方  好不好?</br>
I know a place where we can spend some time together.

01:28:13.560 --> 01:28:16.620
有时候我想我应该娶 像你老婆一样的女人</br>
Sometimes I think I should have married a woman like you did.

01:28:16.760 --> 01:28:23.430
像凯  有孩子 能和他们一起玩耍</br>
Like Kay.Have kids. Have a family.

01:28:24.310 --> 01:28:26.460
在我生命中能有一次</br>
For once in my life

01:28:26.770 --> 01:28:30.900
我能够像爸爸那样</br>
be more like Pop..

01:28:32.970 --> 01:28:35.570
当个儿子并不容易  弗雷多</br>
It's not easy to be a son, Fredo.

01:28:36.100 --> 01:28:37.730
不容易的</br>
It's not easy.

01:28:37.740 --> 01:28:41.100
妈以前常取笑我说 "你不是我生的"</br>
Mama used to say, "You don't belong to me."

01:28:41.110 --> 01:28:47.270
你是吉普赛人留在门口的 有时候我认为那是真的</br>
"You were left on the doorstep by gypsies."Sometimes I think it's true.

01:28:47.750 --> 01:28:49.980
你不是吉普赛人留下的</br>
You're no gypsy, Fredo.

01:28:51.220 --> 01:28:52.940
麦克  我…</br>
Mikey... I...

01:28:53.190 --> 01:28:55.480
我以前生你的气</br>
I was mad at you.

01:29:02.830 --> 01:29:05.780
为何从前我们不曾 像这样一起共聚</br>
Why didn't we spend time like this before?

01:29:06.560 --> 01:29:08.410
你要喝一杯  对吧?</br>
You want a drink, right?

01:29:08.420 --> 01:29:10.190
侍者</br>
Waiter!

01:29:16.660 --> 01:29:18.360
香蕉大克利酒怎么讲?</br>
How do you say Banana Daquiri?

01:29:18.370 --> 01:29:19.780
