01:48:16.700 --> 01:48:18.390
还不错</br>
It's nice.

01:48:20.940 --> 01:48:22.720
谢谢  艾尔</br>
Thank you, Al.

01:48:23.800 --> 01:48:26.560
艾尔 你们是否能出去一会儿?</br>
Fellows, could you step outside for a minute?

01:48:44.350 --> 01:48:46.010
我哥哥呢?</br>
Where's my brother?

01:48:47.110 --> 01:48:49.510
罗斯坐私人船回来了</br>
Roth got out on a private boat.

01:48:49.520 --> 01:48:50.670
