He's in a hospital in Miami.

01:48:50.680 --> 01:48:53.000
心脏病发作过一次 但复元情况良好</br>
He had a stroke, but recovered okay.

01:48:53.410 --> 01:48:55.270
你的侍卫死了</br>
Your bodyguard is dead.

01:48:55.280 --> 01:48:57.020
我在问弗雷多的事</br>
I asked about Fredo.

01:48:58.020 --> 01:49:01.190
我想他逃出来了 一定在纽约某处</br>
I think he got out. He must be somewhere in New York.

01:49:04.420 --> 01:49:06.020
好吧!</br>
All right.

01:49:07.090 --> 01:49:09.250
我要你和他连络</br>
I want you to get in touch with him.

01:49:10.060 --> 01:49:11.750
我晓得他害怕</br>
I know he's scared.

01:49:11.760 --> 01:49:13.020
