Tell him everything is all right.

01:49:13.030 --> 01:49:15.380
我知道是罗斯唆使他的</br>
Tell him I know Roth misled him.

01:49:15.390 --> 01:49:17.990
他并不知道他们想杀我</br>
That he didn't know they would try to kill me.

01:49:19.560 --> 01:49:21.300
叫他们进来吧!</br>
They can come in now.

01:49:21.900 --> 01:49:23.820
麦克  还有别的事</br>
There was something else.

01:49:24.570 --> 01:49:25.960
什么事?</br>
What?

01:49:32.870 --> 01:49:35.200
说吧!什么事?快说</br>
What? Come on.

01:49:36.600 --> 01:49:39.710
凯小产了!孩子没保住!</br>
Kay had a miscarriage.

01:49:51.880 --> 01:49:53.150
是个男孩吗?</br>
Was it a boy?

01:49:53.160 --> 01:49:54.510
麦克  才三个半月大</br>
At three and a half months.

01:49:54.520 --> 01:49:57.480
你不能直接了当给我答案吗?</br>
Can't you give me a straight answer?!

01:49:57.490 --> 01:49:59.380
是个男孩吗?</br>
Was it a boy?

01:50:01.520 --> 01:50:03.450
我真的不知道</br>
I really don't know.

01:50:14.260 --> 01:50:22.730
可怜的小弗雷多  他得了肺炎</br>
Poor little Fredo, he's got pneumonia.

01:51:06.360 --> 01:51:11.780
年轻人  我听说你 及你的朋友们在偷东西</br>
Young man, I hear you and your friends are stealing goods.

01:51:11.790 --> 01:51:14.490
但你们连套衣服 也没送到我家去</br>
But you don't even send a dress to my house.

01:51:14.500 --> 01:51:16.120
不尊重我</br>
No respect!

01:51:16.130 --> 01:51:18.550
你知道我有三个女儿</br>
You know I've got three daughters.

01:51:18.700 --> 01:51:21.660
这是我的地盘</br>
This is my neighborhood.

01:51:21.670 --> 01:51:25.530
你与你的朋友们 应该对我尊敬些</br>
You and your friends should show me some respect.

01:51:25.540 --> 01:51:29.390
你应该分我一份</br>
You should let me wet my beak a little.

01:51:31.570 --> 01:51:35.930
我听说你与你的朋友们</br>
I hear you and your friends

01:51:36.010 --> 01:51:39.140
每人分得了六百元</br>
cleared $600 each.

01:51:39.150 --> 01:51:43.970
为了你们的安全 每人给我二百元保护费</br>
Give me $200 each, for your own protection.

01:51:43.980 --> 01:51:47.690
那我就忘了这侮辱</br>
And I'll forget the insult.

01:51:48.310 --> 01:51:51.180
你们年轻的混蛋该学习</br>
You young punks have to learn

01:51:51.190 --> 01:51:54.620
尊重像我这一类的人</br>
to respect a man like me!

01:51:55.030 --> 01:51:58.250
否则条子会到你们家去</br>
Otherwise the cops will come to your house.

01:51:58.260 --> 01:52:01.080
那你们的家就被毁了</br>
And your family will be ruined.

01:52:01.320 --> 01:52:04.050
当然  若是我弄错了 你们行窃的金额</br>
Of course if I'm wrong about how much you stole

01:52:04.060 --> 01:52:07.350
我可以少收一点 每人少收一百元</br>
I'll take a little less.And by less,I only mean a hundred bucks less.

01:52:08.870 --> 01:52:11.360
别拒绝我  了解吗?</br>
Now don't refuse me.

01:52:14.630 --> 01:52:18.990
-了解吗?同乡 -我了解</br>
-Understand, paesano? -I understand.

01:52:20.870 --> 01:52:23.900
我与我的朋友们把钱全分了</br>
My friends and I share all the money.

01:52:23.910 --> 01:52:26.370
所以我得先和他们谈</br>
So first, I have to talk to them.

01:52:26.380 --> 01:52:28.840
去和你的朋友们谈谈</br>
Tell your friends

01:52:28.850 --> 01:52:32.770
我要的不多  分一份而已</br>
I don't want a lot. Just enough to wet my beak.

01:52:35.710 --> 01:52:38.110
别怕告诉他们</br>
Don't be afraid to tell them!

01:52:40.550 --> 01:52:42.950
六百元</br>
600 bucks.

01:52:43.890 --> 01:52:45.910
若是我们不付呢?</br>
Suppose we don't pay?

01:52:45.920 --> 01:52:48.310
你知道他们那帮人，泰西欧</br>
You know his gang, Tessio.

01:52:48.320 --> 01:52:49.970
真正的野兽!</br>
Real animals.

01:52:49.980 --> 01:52:53.250
马朗萨拉让范伦奇在这一带混</br>
Maranzalla himself let Fanucci work this neighborhood.

01:52:53.260 --> 01:52:55.750
而且他与条子有来往!</br>
He's got connections with the cops, too.

01:52:55.760 --> 01:52:57.450
我们必须付给他</br>
We have to pay him.

01:52:57.460 --> 01:53:01.660
每人二百元  大家同意吗?</br>
$200 each...everybody agreed?

01:53:05.530 --> 01:53:07.150
我们干嘛得付给他?</br>
Why do we have to pay him?

01:53:07.160 --> 01:53:10.430
维多  这件事交给我们</br>
Vito, leave this to us.

01:53:10.960 --> 01:53:13.760
他只有一个人  我们有三个</br>
He's one person, we're three.

01:53:13.770 --> 01:53:17.060
他有枪  我们也有枪</br>
He's got guns, we've got guns.

01:53:17.070 --> 01:53:20.290
为何要将我们的血汗钱送给他</br>
Why should we give him the money we sweated for?

01:53:20.300 --> 01:53:24.200
这里是他的地盘</br>
This is his neighborhood!

01:53:24.470 --> 01:53:30.110
我认识两个不付钱给范伦奇的</br>
I know two bookies who don't give anything to Fanucci.

01:53:30.680 --> 01:53:38.270
他们不付钱给范伦奇</br>
They don't pay Fanucci.

01:53:38.280 --> 01:53:40.940
若他们不付钱给范伦奇</br>
If they don't pay Fanucci

01:53:40.950 --> 01:53:43.970
就是另外有人为马朗萨拉去收</br>
then somebody else collects for Maranzalla!

01:53:43.980 --> 01:53:48.410
我们若付他钱 他就不会再缠我们了</br>
We'll all be better off if we pay him.

01:53:48.420 --> 01:53:50.060
别担心</br>
Don't worry.

01:54:01.730 --> 01:54:07.320
我现在说的仅止于这个房间</br>
Now what I say stays in this room.

01:54:07.330 --> 01:54:09.330
若是你们俩愿意</br>
If you both like

01:54:09.340 --> 01:54:13.800
为何不每人给我50元付范伦奇</br>
why not give me $50 each to pay Fanucci?

01:54:15.470 --> 01:54:19.760
我保证他会接受我付给他的</br>
I guarantee he'll accept what I give him.

01:54:21.940 --> 01:54:23.830
若是范伦奇说二百元</br>
If Fanucci says $200

01:54:23.840 --> 01:54:25.830
他就是要那么多  维多</br>
he means it, Vito!

01:54:25.840 --> 01:54:28.000
我会和他讲道理</br>
I'll reason with him.

01:54:28.310 --> 01:54:33.440
把事情交给我吧!</br>
Leave everything to me.

01:54:33.450 --> 01:54:35.470
我会料理一切的</br>
I'll take care of everything.

01:54:35.480 --> 01:54:40.550
我从不对我的朋友说谎</br>
I never lie to my friends.

01:54:40.560 --> 01:54:44.340
明天你们俩都去和范伦奇谈</br>
Tomorrow you both go talk to Fanucci.

01:54:44.350 --> 01:54:46.640
他会要那笔钱</br>
He'll ask for the money.

01:54:46.650 --> 01:54:51.450
告诉他你们会如数奉上</br>
Tell him you'll pay whatever he wants.

01:54:51.460 --> 01:54:53.250
别和他争论</br>
Don't argue with him.

01:54:53.260 --> 01:54:55.050
然后我会去让他同意</br>
Then I'll go and get him to agree.

01:54:55.060 --> 01:55:02.150
既然他那么强硬  别和他争论</br>
Don't argue with him, since he's so tough.

01:55:02.160 --> 01:55:04.890
你怎么可能让他少拿点?</br>
How can you get him to take less?

01:55:04.900 --> 01:55:07.190
那是我的事</br>
That's my business.

01:55:07.500 --> 01:55:11.630
只要记得我帮了你们一个忙</br>
Just remember that I did you a favor.

01:55:15.340 --> 01:55:19.540
-一言为定? -好</br>
-Is it a deal? -Si.

01:55:25.880 --> 01:55:27.180
干杯!</br>
Salute.

01:55:27.190 --> 01:55:29.410
干杯!</br>
Salute.

01:56:06.800 --> 01:56:09.430
他的家人出去了</br>
His family's out of the house.

01:56:09.440 --> 01:56:11.760
范伦奇一个人在咖啡厅里</br>
Fanucci's alone in the cafe.

01:56:16.640 --> 01:56:21.200
维多  这是我的50元</br>
Vito, here's my 50 dollars.

01:56:30.220 --> 01:56:34.740
维多!你确定他会收吗?</br>
Buona fortuna,are you sure he's going to go for it?

01:56:35.480 --> 01:56:40.480
我会让范伦奇不能拒绝</br>
I'll make an offer he don't refuse.

01:56:40.490 --> 01:56:42.260
别担心</br>
Don't worry.

01:57:14.750 --> 01:57:21.280
看起来我帽子下有一百元</br>
It looks like there's - $100 under my hat.

01:57:31.620 --> 01:57:37.940
我说对了  只有一百元</br>
I was right.Only $100...

01:57:39.990 --> 01:57:43.920
我目前缺钱用</br>
I'm short of money right now.

01:57:43.930 --> 01:57:49.420
我失业了  给我一点时间</br>
I've been out of work,so just give me a little time.

01:57:49.430 --> 01:57:52.790
你了解的  对吧?</br>
You understand, don't you?

01:58:00.360 --> 01:58:04.500
你有胆量  年轻人</br>
You've got balls, young man!

01:58:04.970 --> 01:58:08.560
我以前为何没听到你的名字?</br>
How come I never heard of you before?

01:58:14.450 --> 01:58:18.330
你非常有胆量</br>
You've got a lot of guts.

01:58:20.920 --> 01:58:24.510
我会帮你找份赚大钱的工作</br>
I'll find you some work for good money.

01:58:34.990 --> 01:58:40.020
不伤感情  对吧?</br>
No hard feelings, right?

01:58:42.130 --> 01:58:45.620
若我能帮你  让我晓得</br>
If I can help you, let me know.

01:58:48.130 --> 01:58:50.720
祝你佳节愉快</br>
Enjoy the festa!

01:59:07.910 --> 01:59:09.730
范伦奇阁下</br>
Don FANUCCI.

02:00:52.700 --> 02:00:54.520
好极了…</br>
Forzzelando!

02:01:02.870 --> 02:01:05.040
这对我来说太暴力了</br>
Oh, this is too violent for me!

02:03:24.800 --> 02:03:27.050
你在这里干什么?</br>
What've you got there?

02:06:03.690 --> 02:06:13.980
麦克  爸爸非常的爱你</br>
Michael, your father loves you very much.

02:09:34.320 --> 02:09:37.650
奇契先生  从1942年到现在</br>
Mr. Cicci, from the year 1942 to the present time,

02:09:37.950 --> 02:09:40.940
你是杰安可橄榄油公司的职员</br>
you were an employee of the Genco Olive Oil Company?

02:09:41.410 --> 02:09:43.080
没错</br>
That's right.

02:09:43.940 --> 02:09:45.130
但事实上</br>
But in actuality

02:09:45.140 --> 02:09:48.630
你是柯里昂犯罪组织的成员</br>
you were a member of the Corleone crime organisation.

02:09:51.010 --> 02:09:53.790
不  我们叫做柯里昂家族</br>
No, we called it the Corleone family,

02:09:53.800 --> 02:09:55.390
参议员  我们称之为家族</br>
Senator.we called it the family.

02:09:55.400 --> 02:09:57.320
你的职务是什么?</br>
What was your position?

02:09:58.630 --> 02:10:01.910
起初跟其他人一样 只是个打手</br>
At first, like everybody else, I was a soldier.

02:10:01.920 --> 02:10:03.050
那是什么?</br>
What is that?

02:10:03.060 --> 02:10:05.050
一颗枪子儿  你知道是什么 参议员</br>
A button, you know, Senator.

02:10:05.060 --> 02:10:08.150
不  我不知道  告诉我</br>
No, I don't know. Tell me.

02:10:09.120 --> 02:10:11.850
当老板说给某人一颗枪子儿时</br>
When the boss says "push a button" on a guy,

02:10:11.860 --> 02:10:13.350
我就给他一颗枪子儿</br>
I push a button.

02:10:13.360 --> 02:10:14.710
明白吗?参议员</br>
See, Senator?

02:10:14.720 --> 02:10:16.380
奎斯特先生</br>
Mr. Questadt.

02:10:16.510 --> 02:10:19.040
-你是说你杀人 -我什么?</br>
-You mean you kill people? -?

02:10:19.050 --> 02:10:24.780
你服从上级的命令去杀人</br>
You kill people at the behest of your superiors.

02:10:27.680 --> 02:10:29.290
没错!大律师!</br>
Yeah, that's right.

02:10:29.300 --> 02:10:34.720
而你们家族的 老大是麦克柯里昂</br>
And the head of your family is Michael Corleone?

02:10:34.730 --> 02:10:37.920
是  大律师 麦克柯里昂  对了</br>
Yeah, Counsellor. Michael Corleone.

02:10:37.930 --> 02:10:39.520
你是否有直接收到</br>
Did you ever get such an order

02:10:39.530 --> 02:10:41.520
麦克柯里昂下的命令?</br>
directly from Michael Corleone?

02:10:42.490 --> 02:10:44.680
没有  我从来没和他说过话</br>
No, I never talked to him.

02:10:44.690 --> 02:10:46.290
奇契先生</br>
Mr. Cicci

02:10:46.380 --> 02:10:48.790
你是否能详细说明你的答案?</br>
Could you amplify your answer a bit?

02:10:49.080 --> 02:10:50.640
要我做什么?</br>
Do what?

02:10:50.650 --> 02:10:52.900
你是否能回答得更详细</br>
Could you expand on your answer?

02:10:52.910 --> 02:10:57.970
尤其是是否你跟上级之间 永远有中间人</br>
I'm particularly interested in knowing, was there always a buffer involved?

02:10:58.110 --> 02:11:02.930
在你和发出实际命令的 上级间的中间人</br>
Someone in between you and your superiors who gave the order.

02:11:02.940 --> 02:11:04.930
是  对的  中间人</br>
Right, a buffer.

02:11:04.940 --> 02:11:07.200
家族中有许多的中间人</br>
The family had a lot of buffers!

02:11:08.610 --> 02:11:10.630
奇契先生 你也许觉得这很好玩</br>
You may find this very amusing,

02:11:10.640 --> 02:11:13.730
但我告诉你 委员会的成员不这么想</br>
but the members of this committee do not.

02:11:48.090 --> 02:11:53.510
告诉我  妈  在父亲内心深处 他想些什么?</br>
Tell me something, Ma.What did Papa think deep in his heart?

02:11:57.920 --> 02:12:01.250
他以前很坚强</br>
He was being strong.

02:12:03.090 --> 02:12:09.730
为他的家庭而坚强</br>
Strong for his family.

02:12:12.070 --> 02:12:20.860
可是为他的家坚强以外</br>
But by being strong for his family

02:12:22.110 --> 02:12:27.800
他会不会失去它?</br>
could he lose it?

02:12:28.970 --> 02:12:32.430
你在想你太太及失去的孩子</br>
You're thinking about your wife about the baby you lost.

02:12:32.440 --> 02:12:40.740
但你与你太太都还能再生孩子</br>
But you and your wife can always have another baby.

02:12:40.750 --> 02:12:46.920
不  我是说…失去他的家</br>
No, I meant... lose his family,

02:12:47.550 --> 02:12:54.310
但你永远不会失去你的家</br>
But you can never lose your family.

02:13:00.420 --> 02:13:02.810
时代变了!</br>
Times are changing.

02:13:24.500 --> 02:13:28.030
不  是我的荣幸  不要钱</br>
It's my pleasure. I don't want money.

02:13:28.040 --> 02:13:31.620
-把它当礼物吧! -谢谢  非常谢谢</br>
-Take it as a gift.-

02:13:31.630 --> 02:13:36.840
如果有什么我可以帮忙的 你来  我们谈谈</br>
If there's something I can do for you, you come, we talk.

02:13:37.300 --> 02:13:39.200
谢谢…</br>
Grazie.

02:13:53.080 --> 02:13:57.440
柯伦波太太 你找我有什么事?</br>
Signora Colombo, why did you come to see me?

02:13:59.250 --> 02:14:05.510
你太太叫我来问你是否能帮我</br>
Your wife told me to ask if you could help me.

02:14:05.520 --> 02:14:08.210
她有大麻烦</br>
She's in bad trouble.

02:14:08.220 --> 02:14:12.410
他的邻居向房东抱怨她的狗</br>
Her neighbors complained to the landlord about her dog.

02:14:13.550 --> 02:14:16.510
他叫她把动物丢掉</br>
He told her to get rid of the animal.

02:14:16.520 --> 02:14:20.050
但她的小儿子爱那条狗</br>
But her little boy loves that dog.

02:14:20.060 --> 02:14:22.620
所以她留下了它</br>
So she hid it.

02:14:22.630 --> 02:14:25.180
但当房东发现之后</br>
When the landlord found out

02:14:25.190 --> 02:14:27.220
他很生气  叫她搬走</br>
he got mad and told her to leave.

02:14:27.230 --> 02:14:32.360
现在即使她把狗送走 也无法住下去了</br>
Now she can't stay even if she gets rid of it.

02:14:32.370 --> 02:14:34.630
我好惭愧</br>
I'm so ashamed!

02:14:34.640 --> 02:14:41.020
他说要叫警察把我们扔到街上</br>
He said he'd get the police to throw us out on the street.

02:14:41.840 --> 02:14:46.060
我很抱歉  但…</br>
I'm sorry, but...

02:14:46.070 --> 02:14:49.830
我能给你一些钱帮你搬家</br>
I could give you a couple dollars to help you move.

02:14:49.840 --> 02:14:52.230
我不能搬</br>
I can't move!

02:14:52.410 --> 02:14:55.130
我要你和他谈谈</br>
I want you to talk to him!

02:14:55.140 --> 02:14:58.300
告诉他我希望住在这里</br>
Tell him I want to stay here!

02:15:05.640 --> 02:15:07.470
你的房东叫什么名字?</br>
What's your landlord's name?

02:15:07.480 --> 02:15:10.110
他是罗勃特先生</br>
His name is Signor Roberto.

02:15:10.120 --> 02:15:13.150
他住在第四街  离这很近</br>
He lives on Fourth Street, near here.

02:15:13.280 --> 02:15:17.010
他们打破窗户  弄脏地板</br>
They break the windows, they dirty the floors...

02:15:17.020 --> 02:15:19.510
真是猪  对吧?</br>
A real pig-sty, eh?

02:15:31.230 --> 02:15:34.040
罗勃特先生</br>
Mr.Roberto

02:15:36.600 --> 02:15:39.550
我是维多柯里昂</br>
My name is Vito Corleone.

02:15:39.560 --> 02:15:42.960
柯伦波太太是内人的朋友</br>
Signora Colombo is a friend of my wife.

02:15:42.970 --> 02:15:46.930
她说没有正当理由 就要赶她搬家</br>
She says she's been evicted for no good reason.

02:15:46.940 --> 02:15:50.890
她是个穷寡妇  没人照料她</br>
She's a poor widow, she has nobody to take care of her.

02:15:50.900 --> 02:15:54.130
她没有亲人  没有钱</br>
She has no relatives,no money.

02:15:54.140 --> 02:15:55.690
她所有的只是这一带的邻居</br>
All she has is this neighborhood.

02:15:55.700 --> 02:15:59.660
我已经把那地方租给别人家了</br>
I already rented the place to another family.

02:16:03.600 --> 02:16:06.960
我告诉过她我会和你谈谈</br>
I told her that I'd talk to you.

02:16:06.970 --> 02:16:10.140
而你是个讲道理的人</br>
That you're a reasonable man.

02:16:10.880 --> 02:16:14.870
她已经弄走惹麻烦的狗了</br>
She got rid of the animal that caused all the trouble.

02:16:14.880 --> 02:16:17.730
让她留下来吧!</br>
So let her stay.

02:16:19.780 --> 02:16:23.250
-你是不是西西里人? -不  我是卡拉布列兹人</br>
-Are you Sicilian?-No, I'm Calabrese.

02:16:23.720 --> 02:16:27.410
我们实际上是同乡 帮我一个忙</br>
We're practically paesani, do me this favor.

02:16:27.420 --> 02:16:32.380
我已经租出去了  反悔的话 我会看起来像个白痴</br>
I already rented it! I'll look like an idiot.

02:16:32.390 --> 02:16:34.280
而且新房客的房租要高一些</br>
Besides, the new tenants pay more rent.

02:16:34.290 --> 02:16:37.080
一个月多少钱?</br>
How much more a month?

02:16:37.090 --> 02:16:39.650
五块钱</br>
Five bucks.

02:16:43.730 --> 02:16:46.290
这里是先付六个月的涨价租金</br>
Here's six months increase in advance.

02:16:46.460 --> 02:16:50.680
但别告诉她  她的自尊心很强</br>
But don't tell her about it. She's very proud.

02:16:50.690 --> 02:16:53.690
六个月到了再来找我</br>
Come see me in another six months.

02:16:55.160 --> 02:16:58.260
当然  那条狗留下  对吧?</br>
Of course, the dog stays. Right?

02:16:59.000 --> 02:17:00.520
那条狗留下</br>
The dog stays.

02:17:00.530 --> 02:17:08.300
你算什么?来对我下命令?</br>
Who the hell are you to come give me orders?

02:17:08.310 --> 02:17:14.800
小心我把你那 西西里屁股踢上街</br>
Watch out or I'll kick your Sicilian ass right into the street!

02:17:14.810 --> 02:17:20.560
帮我一个忙  我不会忘记的</br>
Do me this favor.I won't forget it.

02:17:20.570 --> 02:17:24.900
向你这一带的朋友打听我</br>
Ask your friends in the neighborhood about me.

02:17:24.910 --> 02:17:32.520
他们会告诉你  我会回报的</br>
They'll tell you I know how to return a favor.

02:17:34.150 --> 02:17:37.070
好一个厉害的傢伙</br>
What a character!

02:17:43.150 --> 02:17:46.520
维多 那个叫罗勃特的房东来了</br>
That landlord is here... Roberto

02:17:46.530 --> 02:17:49.510
专门出租房子那个</br>
the one who owns those ratholes.

02:17:57.290 --> 02:18:01.050
他在这一带一直打听你</br>
He's been asking all around the neighborhood about you.

02:18:03.260 --> 02:18:05.220
谢谢</br>
Grazie.

02:18:07.330 --> 02:18:11.960
希望我没打扰你  维多阁下</br>
I hope I'm not disturbing you, Don Vito.

02:18:11.970 --> 02:18:15.060
有何效劳之处?罗勃阁下</br>
What can I do for you, Don Roberto?

02:18:15.200 --> 02:18:19.300
真是场误会!圣母玛丽亚</br>
What a misunderstanding! Holy Mary!

02:18:19.440 --> 02:18:24.960
柯伦波太太当然能留下来</br>
Of course Signora Colombo can stay!

02:18:25.340 --> 02:18:27.430
谢谢!…</br>
Grazie...

02:18:27.440 --> 02:18:33.500
维多阁下 我要把你给我的钱还你</br>
I'm giving back the money you gave me.

02:18:33.510 --> 02:18:39.970
一、二、三、四、五、六 全都在这</br>
Un, due, three, four, five, six, tutt'!

02:18:39.980 --> 02:18:45.710
维多阁下  毕竟钱非一切</br>
Because after all, Don Vito, money isn't everything.

02:18:53.390 --> 02:18:55.210
我能坐下吗?</br>
Can I sit down?

02:18:56.320 --> 02:18:57.970
谢谢</br>
Grazie.

02:18:57.980 --> 02:19:01.820
你对寡妇的仁慈令我自己惭愧</br>
Your kindness to that widow made me ashamed of myself.

02:19:01.830 --> 02:19:05.650
房租和以前一样</br>
The rent stays like before!

02:19:13.230 --> 02:19:18.770
而且…我会降价</br>
I'll even lower it.

02:19:19.190 --> 02:19:22.300
我减五元</br>
I'll lower it $5.

02:19:24.600 --> 02:19:26.820
我减十元</br>
I'll lower it $10!

02:19:26.830 --> 02:19:30.900
谢谢…</br>
Grazie...

02:19:30.910 --> 02:19:35.190
我能请你喝咖啡吗?</br>
Can I offer you some coffee?

02:19:35.200 --> 02:19:40.730
我约会快迟到了</br>
I'm late for an appointment!

02:19:40.740 --> 02:19:44.970
这一次不行  也许改天吧!</br>
I can't this time! Ask me another time!

02:19:44.980 --> 02:19:51.970
请原谅我现在失陪了</br>
You'll have to excuse me for now.

02:19:52.280 --> 02:20:00.670
我希望我能留久一点</br>
I wish I could stay longer!

02:20:00.680 --> 02:20:07.150
只要叫我  我就会来的</br>
Just call me and I'll be here!

02:20:07.160 --> 02:20:12.780
谢谢你</br>
Grazie.

02:20:15.950 --> 02:20:20.240
他不会回来了  他会躲起来的</br>
He won't be back. He'll hide out in the Bronx!

02:20:34.800 --> 02:20:37.390
维多  你认为如何?天佑美国</br>
Vito, what do you think?

02:20:37.400 --> 02:20:39.720
我们会鸿图大展的</br>
We'll make a big business!

02:20:46.910 --> 02:20:49.760
-纽约市 -不介意大声点吧?</br>
-New York City.-We'll make a big business!

02:20:50.310 --> 02:20:52.100
纽约市</br>
New York City.

02:20:52.110 --> 02:20:55.870
-你是否为维多柯里昂之子 -是的  我是</br>
- Are you the son of Vito Corleone? - Yes, I am.

02:20:55.910 --> 02:20:57.660
他在哪诞生?</br>
Where was he born?

02:20:57.670 --> 02:20:59.440
西西里的柯里昂村</br>
Corleone, Sicily.

02:20:59.450 --> 02:21:01.740
他是否有时会使用别号</br>
Did he at times use an alias

02:21:01.750 --> 02:21:05.770
就是别人所说的"教父"</br>
that was known in certain circles as Godfather?

02:21:06.310 --> 02:21:09.870
教父是他朋友对他的称呼</br>
Godfather is a term used by his friends.

02:21:09.880 --> 02:21:13.110
是种内心的感受与对他的尊敬</br>
One of affection and respect.

02:21:13.120 --> 02:21:14.480
主席先生!</br>
Mr. Chairman

02:21:14.490 --> 02:21:17.840
我想证实证人的陈词</br>
I would like to verify the witness' statement.

02:21:17.850 --> 02:21:22.910
多年来我的选民中 意大利人后裔不断增加</br>
For years many of my constituents have been of Italian descent.

02:21:23.130 --> 02:21:25.450
而我蛮了解他们</br>
I've come to know them well.

02:21:25.830 --> 02:21:30.210
他们以支持及友谊来荣耀我</br>
They have honoured me with their support and their friendship.

02:21:30.220 --> 02:21:31.680
我可以很骄傲的说</br>
I can proudly say

02:21:31.690 --> 02:21:36.120
我的一些要好的朋友中 有不少是美籍意大利人</br>
that some of my very best friends are Italian-Americans.

02:21:36.590 --> 02:21:41.750
主席先生  在这个重要时刻 我必须离席</br>
However, Mr. Chairman, unfortunately I have to leave these proceedings

02:21:41.760 --> 02:21:44.550
去参加我的委员会</br>
in order to preside over a very important meeting

02:21:44.560 --> 02:21:46.730
主持一个极重要的会议</br>
of my own committee.

02:21:46.800 --> 02:21:50.160
但在我离开之前 我要说明这个</br>
Before I leave, I do want to say this

02:21:50.170 --> 02:21:54.660
这次关于黑手党的听证会 不管怎么样</br>
that these hearings on the Mafia are in no way whatsoever

02:21:54.670 --> 02:21:57.290
都对意大利人是一种侮辱</br>
a slur upon the great Italian people.

02:21:57.300 --> 02:22:00.590
因为根据我自己的 经验与知识我可以断定</br>
I can state from my own knowledge and experience

02:22:00.600 --> 02:22:05.830
美国公民中 最忠贞爱国苦干的人</br>
that Italian-Americans are among the most loyal,most law-abiding,

02:22:05.840 --> 02:22:10.130
美籍意大利人是其中的一分子</br>
patriotic, hard-working American citizens in this land.

02:22:10.380 --> 02:22:15.440
若我们让一粒老鼠屎 坏了一锅粥的话</br>
It would be a shame, Mr. Chairman

02:22:15.450 --> 02:22:18.100
那会是很可惜的  主席先生</br>
if we allowed a few rotten apples to give a bad nameto the whole barrel.

02:22:18.110 --> 02:22:20.870
因为由历史上 伟大的哥伦布时代开始</br>
ecause from the time of Christopher Columbus

02:22:20.880 --> 02:22:23.550
经过了文艺复兴直到目前</br>
to the time of Enrico Fermi

02:22:23.560 --> 02:22:30.540
美籍意大利人一直是我们国家的 前锋与护卫者</br>
Italian-Americans have been pioneers in building and defending our nation.

02:22:30.550 --> 02:22:32.410
他们是土地之盐</br>
They are the salt of the earth

02:22:32.420 --> 02:22:35.520
也是这国家的支柱之一</br>
and one of the backbones of this country.

02:22:38.320 --> 02:22:39.450
这边</br>
Here,

02:22:39.460 --> 02:22:41.780
这边…</br>
Here...

02:22:41.790 --> 02:22:45.420
我想大家都同意我们同僚的话</br>
I think we all agree with our esteemed college.

02:22:45.560 --> 02:22:46.710
柯里昂先生</br>
Now,Mr. Corleone

02:22:46.720 --> 02:22:49.820
你已经被知会了你的法律权益</br>
you have been advised as to your legal rights.

02:22:50.060 --> 02:22:52.080
我们有一位证人的证词</br>
We have testimony

02:22:52.090 --> 02:22:53.350
一位之前的证人</br>
from a previous witness

02:22:53.360 --> 02:22:56.260
奇契先生</br>
one Willi Cicci.

02:22:56.560 --> 02:22:57.990
他作证说你是这国家中</br>
He stated hat you are head of

02:22:58.000 --> 02:23:00.990
最有威力的黑手党家族的老大</br>
the most powerful Mafia family in the country.

02:23:01.000 --> 02:23:03.390
-你是吗? -不  我不是</br>
- Are you? - No, I'm not.

02:23:03.400 --> 02:23:06.920
证人指证你要对1947年 纽约市警官的谋杀案</br>
He testified that you are personally responsible

02:23:06.930 --> 02:23:12.290
及与他一起被杀的 威尔斯索拉索</br>
for the murder of a New York police captain in 1947

02:23:12.300 --> 02:23:14.500
负完全的责任</br>
and with him a man named Virgil Sollozzo.

02:23:14.510 --> 02:23:17.130
-你否认吗? -是的  我否认</br>
- Do you deny this? - Yes, I do.

02:23:17.140 --> 02:23:22.340
1950年时你是否策划杀害</br>
Is it true that in the year 1950 you devised the murder

02:23:22.350 --> 02:23:26.000
所谓纽约市五大家族的老大</br>
of the heads of the "Five Families" in New York

02:23:26.010 --> 02:23:29.680
以稳固你独霸的情况</br>
who assume and consolidate your nefarious power?

02:23:29.690 --> 02:23:31.940
这完全是假的  先生</br>
It's a complete falsehood.

02:23:31.950 --> 02:23:33.210
奎斯特先生</br>
Mr. Questadt.

02:23:33.220 --> 02:23:38.100
你是否拥有 拉斯维加斯三间主要旅馆</br>
Is it true you have a controlling interest in three major hotels in Las Vegas?

02:23:38.720 --> 02:23:39.940
不  不是真的!</br>
No, it's not true.

02:23:39.950 --> 02:23:42.640
我拥有一些那里旅馆的股票</br>
I own some stock in some of the hotels there

02:23:42.650 --> 02:23:44.250
但数量很少</br>
but very little.

02:23:46.760 --> 02:23:51.040
我也有IBM 及电话电报公司的部分股票</br>
I also have stock in IBM and IT&T.

02:23:51.050 --> 02:23:52.180
柯里昂先生</br>
Mr. Corleone

02:23:52.190 --> 02:23:56.480
你是否控制了纽约州的 赌场及毒品市场</br>
Mr. Corleone do you have any interests or control over gambling or narcotics

02:23:56.490 --> 02:23:59.820
-或是有那个兴趣 -不  我没有</br>
-in the state of New York.? -No, I do not.

02:23:59.830 --> 02:24:02.410
参议员  我的委托人想要…</br>
Senator, my client would like

02:24:02.420 --> 02:24:03.620
在这委员会面前发表一篇声明</br>
to read a statement.

02:24:03.630 --> 02:24:04.820
主席先生!</br>
Mr. Chairman

02:24:04.830 --> 02:24:07.190
主席先生!我认为这篇声明</br>
Mr. Chairman,I think this statement is

02:24:07.200 --> 02:24:09.390
以目前来说是完全不合时宜的</br>
totally out of order at this time.

02:24:09.400 --> 02:24:12.430
先生  我的委托人 很诚心诚意的</br>
Sir, my client has answered

02:24:12.440 --> 02:24:13.690
回答了这委员会每一个问题</br>
this committee's questions with sincerity.

02:24:13.700 --> 02:24:17.260
他虽有权引用</br>
He hasn't taken

02:24:17.270 --> 02:24:18.800
但他并没有用 宪法第五修正案来回避</br>
the Fifth Amendment

02:24:18.810 --> 02:24:20.130
为了公平起见</br>
so this statement

02:24:20.140 --> 02:24:21.960
我们认为这篇声明该被听到</br>
should be heard!

02:24:23.210 --> 02:24:26.700
不  我允许柯里昂先生 读出他的声明</br>
No, I'll allow Mr. Corleone to read his statement.

02:24:26.710 --> 02:24:28.770
我会把它列入记录</br>
I'll put it in the record.

02:24:30.010 --> 02:24:32.910
为了希望澄清我家庭的名声</br>
In the hopes of clearing my family name

02:24:33.040 --> 02:24:35.400
怀着真挚的愿望想给我的孩子</br>
to give my children their

02:24:35.410 --> 02:24:37.300
公平的享受一个美国式的生活</br>
share of the American way of life

02:24:37.310 --> 02:24:40.140
使他们的姓氏和背景 不用背负恶名</br>
without a blemish on their name and background

02:24:40.350 --> 02:24:45.870
我出席这委员会 并尽可能的合作</br>
I have appeared before this committee and given it all my cooperation.

02:24:46.890 --> 02:24:52.510
我必须否认我是罪犯 那对我而言是极为不荣誉</br>
I consider it a great personal dishonour to have to deny that I am a criminal.

02:24:53.480 --> 02:24:56.480
我希望以下几点列入记录中</br>
I wish to have the following noted for the record:

02:24:56.950 --> 02:24:58.810
在第二次世界大战时</br>
That I served my country faithfully

02:24:58.820 --> 02:25:01.280
我忠心及荣耀的 为我的国家服务</br>
in World War Two and was awarded

02:25:01.290 --> 02:25:03.640
我因保卫我国家的行动</br>
the Navy Cross for actions

02:25:03.650 --> 02:25:06.350
而获颁海军十字勋章</br>
in defence of my country.

02:25:07.130 --> 02:25:11.420
我从来没有因任何罪名 被捕或定罪</br>
That I have never been arrested or indicted for any crime.

02:25:11.460 --> 02:25:15.390
没有任何证据 使我牵连到犯罪阴谋中</br>
That no proof linking me to any criminal conspiracy

02:25:15.690 --> 02:25:18.760
不管是黑手党或是同乡帮</br>
whether it is called Mafia or Cosa Nostra

02:25:18.770 --> 02:25:22.890
或任何你们想加诸于我的 众所皆知的罪名</br>
or any other name has ever been made public.

02:25:23.060 --> 02:25:26.130
虽然有权利这么做</br>
I have not taken refuge behind the Fifth Amendment

02:25:26.140 --> 02:25:28.330
但我并未以第五修正案 作护身符</br>
although I may do so.

02:25:31.170 --> 02:25:33.420
我向这委员会挑战</br>
I challenge this committee

02:25:33.430 --> 02:25:36.700
请他们提出任何 不利于我的人证或物证</br>
to produce any witness or evidence against me

02:25:36.940 --> 02:25:38.830
若是他们无法提出</br>
and if they do not

02:25:39.370 --> 02:25:41.560
我希望他们以相同情况</br>
I hope they will have the decency

02:25:41.570 --> 02:25:44.800
在大众面前洗清我的名声</br>
to clear my name with the same publicity

02:25:44.810 --> 02:25:47.300
他们现在已完全的 破坏了我的名声</br>
with which they have besmirched it.

02:25:48.040 --> 02:25:50.840
柯里昂先生  我确信我们 都留下了深刻的印象</br>
I'm sure we're all quite impressed.

02:25:50.850 --> 02:25:53.340
尤其是你对国家的爱</br>
Particularly with your love for our country.

02:25:53.550 --> 02:25:56.430
委员会暂停到下周一上午十点</br>
We'll be in recess until 10 a.m. Monday

02:25:56.440 --> 02:25:58.770
那时候本会将提出证人</br>
when we will produce a witness

02:25:58.780 --> 02:26:01.410
以确定今天对你提出的控诉</br>
who'll corroborate the charges against you.

02:26:01.420 --> 02:26:03.040
当时候到了  柯里昂先生</br>
And at which time Mr.Corleone.

02:26:03.050 --> 02:26:06.440
你非常可能会被证明有罪</br>
you may very well be subject to indictment for perjury.

02:26:06.450 --> 02:26:11.270
我提醒你  你必须随传随到 柯里昂先生  休会</br>
I remind you that you're still under subpoena.Adjourned!

02:26:14.960 --> 02:26:17.750
十比一  十比一的机会 你说的</br>
Ten-to-one shot, you said.

02:26:17.760 --> 02:26:19.450
十比一的机会</br>
Ten-to-one shot

02:26:19.460 --> 02:26:22.780
他会采用第五修正案 而我输了</br>
He would take the Fifth, and I lose.

02:26:22.790 --> 02:26:24.950
你听起来像是我的赌马经纪人</br>
You sound like my bookie.

02:26:24.960 --> 02:26:27.390
我欠那傢伙一条命</br>
I owe that monkey my life.

02:26:28.570 --> 02:26:30.420
你最好是好好睡一觉</br>
Well, just get a good night's sleep.

02:26:30.430 --> 02:26:32.020
是  好好的睡</br>
Yeah.

02:26:32.030 --> 02:26:34.160
明天是大日子</br>
You've got a big day tomorrow.

02:26:34.330 --> 02:26:38.330
给你买了新西装 新衬衫和新领带</br>
I've got you a new suit, new shirt, new tie.

02:26:38.740 --> 02:26:41.500
明天我会亲自给你刮胡子</br>
I'll shave you myself in the morning.

02:26:42.140 --> 02:26:44.160
在你五千万名美国同胞面前</br>
You'll look respectable for 50 million

02:26:44.170 --> 02:26:46.230
你会看起来很体面</br>
of your fellow Americans.

02:26:46.240 --> 02:26:51.670
我的命  我的命在明天之后 就一文不值了</br>
Tomorrow... My life won't be worth a nickel after tomorrow.

02:26:52.510 --> 02:26:56.600
得了吧!我看过了 看了19遍了</br>
Come on! I saw this 19 times.

02:26:57.310 --> 02:26:59.770
你的家很漂亮  法兰克</br>
You've got a great home here

02:26:59.950 --> 02:27:02.140
你的余生  没人能接近你</br>
for the rest of your life.Nobody gets near you

02:27:02.150 --> 02:27:03.810
你那里都不能去</br>
you're not going anywhere.

02:27:03.950 --> 02:27:07.110
那好极了  美极了</br>
That's great. Beautiful.

02:27:07.350 --> 02:27:09.480
我做的好交易</br>
Some deal I made.

02:27:09.490 --> 02:27:12.270
你会活的像国王 你会是位英雄</br>
You'll live like a king. You'll be a hero.

02:27:12.280 --> 02:27:15.370
你在这里会比多数 在外面的人要活的好</br>
You'll live better here than most people outside.

02:27:15.380 --> 02:27:17.050
好一个交易</br>
Some deal!

02:27:21.620 --> 02:27:24.720
潘坦居利还活着!</br>
Alive. Pentangeli is alive.

02:27:25.980 --> 02:27:27.880
他们怎会找上他的?</br>
How did they get their hands on him?

02:27:27.890 --> 02:27:32.020
罗斯  是他设计的  麦克</br>
Roth. He engineered it, Michael.

02:27:32.030 --> 02:27:34.580
法兰克想和罗萨多兄弟谈条件</br>
When Frankie went to make a deal with the Rosato brothers

02:27:34.590 --> 02:27:36.580
结果他们想杀了他</br>
they tried to kill him.

02:27:36.590 --> 02:27:38.760
他以为是你出卖了他</br>
He thought you double-crossed him.

02:27:40.030 --> 02:27:42.790
我们在纽约的人说 他已经半死了</br>
Our people with the detectives said he was half dead

02:27:42.800 --> 02:27:45.890
吓得全身僵硬 大声说你出卖了他</br>
scared,and shouted that you'd turned on him.

02:27:46.200 --> 02:27:47.790
他们早就控制他了</br>
They already had him on possession

02:27:47.800 --> 02:27:51.230
做假帐、一级谋杀 还有很多罪名</br>
bookmaking, murder one and more.

02:27:52.330 --> 02:27:55.260
联邦调查局把他看的很紧</br>
The FBI has him airtight.

02:27:55.270 --> 02:27:58.100
留在一个陆军基地里 24小时保护</br>
He's on an army base, 24 hour guards.

02:27:58.110 --> 02:28:01.130
我们想接近他是不可能的</br>
We can't get to him.

02:28:01.140 --> 02:28:03.570
你使自己犯下五项伪证罪</br>
You've opened yourself to five counts of perjury.

02:28:05.540 --> 02:28:08.570
弗雷多呢?他知道什么?</br>
What about Fredo? What does he know?

02:28:08.580 --> 02:28:10.200
他说他什么都不知道</br>
He says he doesn't know anything

02:28:10.210 --> 02:28:11.950
我相信他</br>
and I believe him.

02:28:12.480 --> 02:28:17.380
罗斯!他这一次耍的够漂亮</br>
Roth, he... played this one beautifully.

02:28:24.290 --> 02:28:26.210
我要和弗雷多谈谈</br>
I'm going to talk to Fredo.

02:29:06.100 --> 02:29:08.770
我没有什么好说的  麦克</br>
I haven't got a lot to say, Mike.

02:29:10.410 --> 02:29:12.440
我们有时间</br>
We have time.

02:29:13.080 --> 02:29:16.300
我被蒙在鼓里</br>
I was kept pretty much in the dark.

02:29:17.540 --> 02:29:19.700
我晓得的并不多</br>
I didn't know all that much.

02:29:20.610 --> 02:29:22.430
现在呢?</br>
What about now?

02:29:23.450 --> 02:29:28.770
有没有什么你知道的 可以帮助我?</br>
Is there anything you can help me out with? Anything you can tell me now?

02:29:30.310 --> 02:29:33.340
他们掌握了潘坦居利 我只能告诉你这个</br>
They've got Pentangeli.

02:29:47.550 --> 02:29:50.750
我并不晓得会是暗杀  麦克</br>
I didn't know it was going to be a hit, Mike.

02:29:51.360 --> 02:29:54.550
我对天发誓我不晓得会是暗杀</br>
I swear to God I didn't know.

02:29:56.560 --> 02:29:59.080
强尼欧拉跑来找我</br>
Johnny Ola bumped into me

02:29:59.090 --> 02:30:01.260
在比佛利山</br>
in Beverly Hills.

02:30:02.760 --> 02:30:05.930
他说  他想谈谈</br>
He said that he wanted to talk.

02:30:07.400 --> 02:30:14.570
他说你和罗斯 在合作做宗大买卖</br>
He said that you and Roth were in on a big deal together.

02:30:16.040 --> 02:30:20.360
但若我能帮忙  就算我一份</br>
And that there was something in it for me if I could help him out.

02:30:20.370 --> 02:30:24.460
他说  他说你在协调上 态度很强硬</br>
He said that you were being tough on the negotiations

02:30:24.470 --> 02:30:26.730
但若他们能有点协助</br>
but if they could get a little help

02:30:26.740 --> 02:30:29.330
能很快的完成这笔买卖</br>
and close the deal fast

02:30:30.380 --> 02:30:33.730
那会对家族有益</br>
it would be good for the family.

02:30:34.440 --> 02:30:36.810
你相信他说的鬼话?</br>
And you believed that story?

02:30:37.410 --> 02:30:39.200
你相信那个?</br>
You believed that?

02:30:39.210 --> 02:30:41.770
他说算我一份</br>
He said there was something in it for me

02:30:41.780 --> 02:30:45.510
-我自己的! -我一向都照料你</br>
-on my own! -I've always taken care of you, Fredo.

02:30:45.590 --> 02:30:47.810
照料我?</br>
Taken care of me?!

02:30:48.650 --> 02:30:52.210
你是我弟弟  你照料我?</br>
You're my kid brother!You take care of me?

02:30:52.450 --> 02:30:54.280
你想过那一点吗?</br>
Did you ever think about that?

02:30:54.290 --> 02:30:57.490
你曾想过那一点吗?</br>
Did you ever once think about that?

02:30:57.690 --> 02:30:59.150
叫弗雷多去办这个</br>
Send Fredo off to do this

02:30:59.160 --> 02:31:01.650
叫弗雷多去办那个</br>
send Fredo off to do that!

02:31:02.460 --> 02:31:07.050
让弗雷多打理 某处的无名夜总会</br>
Let Fredo take care of some Mickey Mouse nightclub somewhere.

02:31:07.060 --> 02:31:10.320
叫弗雷多去机场接某个人</br>
Let Fredo fetch somebody at the airport!

02:31:10.330 --> 02:31:11.850
我是你哥哥  麦克</br>
I'm your older brother

02:31:11.860 --> 02:31:13.590
而我却被你踏在脚下</br>
but was stepped over!

02:31:13.600 --> 02:31:17.090
-那是爸爸的意思 -但那不是我要的</br>
- It's the way Pop wanted it.- It's not the way I wanted it!

02:31:18.000 --> 02:31:20.920
我能处理事情  我够精明</br>
I can handle things, I'm smart!

02:31:20.930 --> 02:31:23.990
不像是每个人所说的我很笨</br>
Not like everybody says.

02:31:24.000 --> 02:31:27.170
我很精明  我要被尊重</br>
Like dumb. I'm smart and I want respect!

02:31:34.870 --> 02:31:38.670
对这件调查 你能告诉我什么吗?</br>
Is there anything you can tell me about this investigation?

02:31:38.680 --> 02:31:40.560
任何一点点?</br>
Anything more?

02:31:47.940 --> 02:31:54.900
他们所选用的律师奎斯特 是罗斯的人</br>
The senate lawyer, Questadt... He belongs to Roth.

02:32:03.790 --> 02:32:05.350
弗雷多</br>
Fredo...

02:32:07.850 --> 02:32:10.210
现在你对我什么也不是?</br>
...you're nothing to me now.

02:32:12.430 --> 02:32:16.450
你不是哥哥  也不是朋友</br>
Not a brother, not a friend.

02:32:16.520 --> 02:32:19.520
我不想知道你及你的所作所为</br>
I don't want to know you, or what you do.

02:32:20.890 --> 02:32:23.160
我不想看见你在旅馆中</br>
I don't want to see you at the hotels.

02:32:23.860 --> 02:32:26.630
我不想你接近我的房子</br>
I don't want you near my house.

02:32:28.360 --> 02:32:33.420
当你要见母亲时  先通知我 好让我避开</br>
When you see our mother, I want to know in advance, so I won't be there.

02:32:34.560 --> 02:32:36.620
了解吗?</br>
You understand?

02:32:46.170 --> 02:32:48.200
麦克</br>
Mikey.

02:32:54.510 --> 02:32:58.940
在家母还活着的时候 我不要他发生任何事</br>
I don't want anything to happen to him while my mother's alive.

02:33:48.830 --> 02:33:51.500
这里比球赛的人还要多</br>
There's more people than at a ballgame in here.

02:33:52.200 --> 02:33:54.700
威力奇契在那里</br>
Hey, there's Willi Cicci!

02:34:16.110 --> 02:34:18.880
请保持秩序</br>
This committee will come to order!

02:34:21.220 --> 02:34:22.710
请说你的姓名</br>
State your name, please.

02:34:22.720 --> 02:34:24.240
法兰克潘坦居利</br>
Frank Pentangeli.

02:34:24.250 --> 02:34:25.410
你的出生地?</br>
Where were you born?

02:34:25.420 --> 02:34:27.970
庞特耐格罗  在巴勒摩的外围</br>
Pontenegro, it's outside of Palermo.

02:34:27.980 --> 02:34:29.770
你现在住在哪里?</br>
Where do you live now?

02:34:30.250 --> 02:34:35.040
我和联邦调查局的人 住在陆军营舍中</br>
I live in an army barracks with the FBI guys.

02:34:36.420 --> 02:34:39.080
我们在这终于有一位证人</br>
We have here a witness

02:34:39.090 --> 02:34:42.280
能进一步的作证 指出麦克柯里昂</br>
that will further testify,to Michael Corleone's

02:34:42.290 --> 02:34:44.420
是这犯罪王国的统领</br>
rule of a criminal empire

02:34:44.430 --> 02:34:47.890
控制全国所有的赌博 也许还有别的国家</br>
that controls all gambling.

02:34:47.900 --> 02:34:49.920
这位证人与麦克柯里昂之间</br>
This witness has had no buffer

02:34:49.930 --> 02:34:52.650
没有中间人</br>
between himself and Michael Corleone.

02:34:52.660 --> 02:34:53.920
他能合作</br>
He can corroborate enough charges

02:34:53.930 --> 02:34:55.850
我们的控诉就有足够的证据</br>
for us to recommend

02:34:55.860 --> 02:34:56.920
让这委员会</br>
a charge of perjury

02:34:56.930 --> 02:35:00.930
能对麦克柯里昂的罪进行诉讼</br>
against Michael Corleone.

02:35:00.940 --> 02:35:03.530
-参议员 -谢谢你  吉姆</br>
- Senator. - Thank you, Chairman.

02:35:04.240 --> 02:35:06.390
潘坦居利先生</br>
Mr. Pentangeli...

02:35:07.140 --> 02:35:09.370
潘坦居利先生</br>
Mr. Pentangeli.

02:35:09.570 --> 02:35:12.600
你是柯里昂家族的一员吗?</br>
Were you a member of the Corleone family?

02:35:12.810 --> 02:35:18.000
你是否为下述人作事? 卡波瑞金  彼得克里曼沙</br>
Did you serve under Caporegime, Peter Clemenza,

02:35:18.010 --> 02:35:22.710
还有人称教父的维多柯里昂</br>
and under Vito Corleone,also known as the Godfather?

02:35:28.350 --> 02:35:31.620
我…我从来不认得教父</br>
I never knew any Godfather.

02:35:33.520 --> 02:35:36.370
我有我自己的家族  参议员</br>
I have my own family.

02:35:39.020 --> 02:35:41.110
潘坦居利先生  你是…</br>
Mr. Pentangeli, you...

02:35:41.490 --> 02:35:43.680
你在驳斥自己的宣誓笔录</br>
You are contradicting

02:35:43.690 --> 02:35:46.310
与你原先所做的 并且签了字的大相矛盾</br>
your own sworn statement.

02:35:46.320 --> 02:35:48.150
我再问你一次  先生</br>
I ask you again, sir

02:35:48.160 --> 02:35:49.880
此时此地在这情况下</br>
here and now under oath,

02:35:49.890 --> 02:35:56.250
你曾经是以麦克柯里昂 为首的犯罪组织的成员吗?</br>
were you at any time a member of a crime organisation led by Michael Corleone?

02:35:56.260 --> 02:35:58.320
我对那点一无所知</br>
I don't know nothing about that!

02:36:02.090 --> 02:36:06.090
我和他的父亲 曾在橄榄油事业共事过</br>
I was in the olive oil business with his father

02:36:06.200 --> 02:36:09.590
但那是很久以前了  如此而已</br>
but that was a long time ago.

02:36:10.030 --> 02:36:13.190
我们有份你宣誓的笔录</br>
We have a sworn affidavit.

02:36:13.190 --> 02:36:16.290
我们有你的宣誓口供</br>
Your sworn affidavit

02:36:16.300 --> 02:36:19.430
指出你奉麦克柯里昂之命 去谋杀人</br>
that you murdered on the orders of Michael Corleone.

02:36:19.440 --> 02:36:21.400
你否认那份自白书吗?</br>
Do you deny this confession

02:36:21.410 --> 02:36:24.190
你是否了解 你的否认会有何结果</br>
and do you realise what will happen if you do?

02:36:24.200 --> 02:36:27.330
调查局的人答应我个条件</br>
The FBI guys promised me a deal

02:36:27.340 --> 02:36:31.240
所以我假造很多 麦克柯里昂的事</br>
so I made up a lot of stuff about Michael Corleone

02:36:31.250 --> 02:36:33.270
因为那是他们想要的</br>
just to please them.

02:36:33.280 --> 02:36:35.570
但…那全是谎言</br>
But it was all lies.

02:36:35.640 --> 02:36:38.100
全都是</br>
Everything!

02:36:38.110 --> 02:36:42.940
他们不停的说 麦克柯里昂做了这个</br>
They kept saying,"Michael Corleone did this"

02:36:42.950 --> 02:36:46.010
麦克柯里昂做了那个</br>
and "Michael Corleone did that".

02:36:46.790 --> 02:36:51.110
所以我说  是 当然  有何不可</br>
So I said, "Yeah, sure. Why not?"

02:36:51.120 --> 02:36:52.600
柯里昂先生</br>
Mr. Corleone

02:36:52.610 --> 02:36:55.240
你是否能告诉本委员</br>
would you kindly identify

02:36:55.250 --> 02:36:57.310
坐在你左边的那一位是谁?</br>
the gentleman sitting to your left?

02:36:57.320 --> 02:36:59.020
我能回答</br>
I can answer that.

02:36:59.660 --> 02:37:02.780
他的名字是文森卓潘坦居利</br>
His name is Vincenzo Pentangeli.

02:37:02.920 --> 02:37:05.210
他是否和证人有关系</br>
Is he related to the witness?

02:37:05.590 --> 02:37:07.620
是  我相信是他的哥哥</br>
He is, I believe, his brother.

02:37:07.830 --> 02:37:10.210
他能到前来宣誓吗?</br>
Will he come forward and be sworn?

02:37:10.260 --> 02:37:12.660
先生  这个人不了解英文</br>
He doesn't understand English.

02:37:12.670 --> 02:37:13.780
他自费来此</br>
He came at his own expense

02:37:13.790 --> 02:37:16.320
在他弟弟有难时伸出援手</br>
to aid his brother.

02:37:16.330 --> 02:37:19.090
他没有收到传票 而且他在他自己国家内的名誉</br>
He's not under subpoena,and his reputation in his own country

02:37:19.100 --> 02:37:20.220
是相当受尊重的</br>
is impeccable.

02:37:20.230 --> 02:37:22.090
你是说他对这些事一无所知</br>
He knows nothing about this?

02:37:22.100 --> 02:37:24.060
据我了解是一无所知</br>
To my knowledge, nothing.

02:37:24.070 --> 02:37:26.820
我要弄清楚这里是怎么一回事</br>
I'm going to find out what happened!

02:37:26.830 --> 02:37:29.150
现在休会</br>
This committee is now adjourned.

02:37:29.160 --> 02:37:30.390
证人可以退席了</br>
The witness is excused.

02:37:30.400 --> 02:37:31.800
参议员!</br>
Senator!

02:37:32.210 --> 02:37:33.360
参议员!</br>
Senator!

02:37:33.370 --> 02:37:36.070
这个委员会应该道歉</br>
This committee owes an apology!

02:37:36.380 --> 02:37:40.730
这个委员会应该道歉 参议员</br>
This committee owes an apology. Apology, Senator!

02:38:07.920 --> 02:38:12.480
-麦克!打扰一下 -亲爱的</br>
- Michael, excuse me. - Hello, darling.

02:38:12.490 --> 02:38:15.250
孩子们在外面  我们要走了</br>
The children are outside. We're going.

02:38:17.220 --> 02:38:20.180
你要去哪?我们要回农场</br>
What do you mean? We're leaving tomorrow.

02:38:21.060 --> 02:38:26.530
-罗可 -需要我时再叫我</br>
-Rocco?-I'll be in my room, Mike.

02:38:29.530 --> 02:38:32.230
麦克  我不回内华达</br>
Michael, I'm not going back to Nevada.

02:38:32.600 --> 02:38:35.790
我带孩子们来向你说再见</br>
I brought the children to say goodbye to you.

02:38:39.200 --> 02:38:41.920
我要你知道我为你高兴</br>
I'm very happy for you.

02:38:41.930 --> 02:38:44.620
我想我一直都知道 你太精明了</br>
I always knew you were too smart

02:38:44.630 --> 02:38:47.130
不会让他们击败你</br>
to let any of them beat you.

02:38:47.910 --> 02:38:52.570
-坐下吧! -不  我不想久留  不行</br>
- Why don't you sit down? - No, I'm not going to stay long.

02:38:52.580 --> 02:38:54.870
有些事我想和你谈谈</br>
There are some things I'd like to talk to you about.

02:38:56.880 --> 02:38:59.260
我心理有些事</br>
Things that have been on my mind

02:39:00.220 --> 02:39:01.800
某些我想做的改变</br>
changes I want to make.

02:39:01.810 --> 02:39:05.080
